{"1":[[367,525,"You also have a fitting"],[525,642,"for the garden party."],[642,788,"Followed by the charity photo shoot."],[834,1026,"Oh, and Sir Elton John would like"],[1026,1180,"to pop around and say hello."],[1209,1393,"Pop around to say hello?"],[1393,1488,"You give someone a title, and they"],[1488,1655,"treat the place like it’s a Starbucks."],[1655,1705,"Quite."],[1810,1897,"“The Queen is..."],[1897,2072,"unfortunately indisposed.”"],[2072,2227,"Now, at half-past twelve..."],[2227,2444,"Okay, Just give me the book, Lucius."],[2827,3003,"Are you ready, Your Majesty?"],[3082,3211,"Of course, I'm ready."],[3274,3407,"I'm the Queen Of England."],[3407,3541,"When am I not ready?"],[5780,5976,"Yes, of course, get on with it."],[5976,6181,"Really, what's the point?"],[6181,6393,"It's a race, you idiot!"],[6477,6610,"Oooh!"],[6710,6944,"I mean, it's a race, you idiot,"],[6944,7082,"Your Royal Highness."],[7107,7378,"It's a race. True enough."],[7453,7549,"But some things in life"],[7549,7657,"are meant to be savored."],[7736,7828,"A cold drink."],[8479,8692,"Time with your mates."],[9384,9584,"The woman in your bed."]],"2":[[51,247,"Damn, that feels good."],[435,606,"Let me ask you something."],[606,710,"Could, uh..."],[798,906,"Could we go somewhere"],[1002,1106,"without them?"],[1461,1544,"Sorry, umm..."],[1544,1686,"What did you have in mind?"],[1686,1786,"Paris?"],[1915,2074,"I was thinking more like your bed."],[2149,2291,"Oh, I like that even better."],[2512,2608,"But..."],[2641,2737,"Can we really go to Paris?"],[2783,2933,"Sure. My sister's there right now."],[3626,3876,"Bitch, your coked up ass better curtsy."],[4401,4514,"Do we like them?"],[4622,4685,"No."],[10253,10395,"Your Majesty."],[10666,10774,"My God, Truman."],[10774,10904,"What else did she do?"],[11016,11075,"I can't imagine"],[11075,11191,"it can get any worse."],[11279,11437,"It's not your daughter, sir."],[11625,11721,"It's your son."],[11942,12064,"I'm afraid it is worse."]],"3":[[864,943,"Prince Liam?"],[1022,1156,"Marcus."],[1201,1281,"You're supposed to guard me,"],[1281,1385,"not scare the hell out of me."],[1422,1527,"You need to return to the palace,"],[1527,1619,"Your Highness."],[1765,1844,"Why? What's going on?"],[1844,1965,"You too, Ophelia."],[2811,2916,"Mum."],[2970,3153,"\"Eleanorgy.\""],[3153,3341,"\"Flash Dance.\""],[3341,3554,"\"Royal Beaver.\""],[4033,4271,"My daughter, the Princess,"],[4271,4455,"behaving like a common whore."],[4526,4709,"But go on, amuse me."],[4709,4847,"Explain this latest disgrace."],[4847,4993,"But, please, Eleanor,"],[5047,5185,"make it original this time."],[5414,5652,"Robert's dead, Mum."],[7299,7691,"I'll never forget the look on his face."],[7691,7821,"The bewildered boy who had"],[7821,7987,"just lost his brother."],[8621,8797,"And in the same moment"],[8797,8901,"had become the future"],[8901,9018,"King Of England."]],"4":[[1156,1231,"The body is where?"],[1414,1531,"And he won't be moved, right?"],[1990,2148,"Military protocol's in our favor."],[2198,2278,"It's imperative things"],[2278,2415,"remain anonymous and unremarkable."],[2415,2507,"Fiona will handle press."],[2507,2615,"I'll personally escort the body."],[2674,2774,"Yeah. I'm on my way."],[2824,2907,"How'd it happen?"],[3007,3145,"We're still gathering information."],[3216,3366,"Is that the truth from my father,"],[3366,3508,"or the official response from"],[3508,3666,"the King's Head of Security?"],[3679,3771,"The truth from your father."],[3804,3879,"The same father who"],[3879,3950,"went to your room"],[3950,4071,"to find your bed empty,"],[4109,4275,"which can't be said for the Prince's bed."],[4275,4367,"A fact I had to learn"],[4367,4463,"from one of my own men."],[4463,4501,"I know."],[4501,4684,"Just don't take it out on Marcus, okay?"],[4734,4801,"He didn't know."],[4801,4909,"When the Queen asks her"],[4909,4997,"Head of Security"],[4997,5205,"why he can't control his own daughter,"],[5205,5318,"what would you like me to say?"],[5318,5397,"I don't know."],[5397,5535,"You could tell her that your normally"],[5535,5631,"somewhat responsible daughter"],[5631,5860,"daughter got drunk on gin and tonics,"],[5860,5935,"mostly gin,"],[5935,6048,"and had irresponsible"],[6048,6219,"but protected sex with her son."],[6277,6419,"And is very much ashamed of herself."],[6899,7057,"I'm an employee, Ophelia."],[7128,7303,"We live here under an unspoken code"],[7303,7437,"of distance and division."],[7437,7604,"A code you must have conveniently"],[7604,7695,"forgotten, otherwise you wouldn't have"],[7695,7879,"been up all night drinking mostly gin"],[7912,8025,"and having illicit sex with the"],[8025,8092,"future King of England."],[8138,8246,"You're absolutely right."],[8329,8421,"I'm sorry."],[8530,8684,"And I'm sorry about Robert."],[8763,9022,"I'm disappointed in you. Go to class."],[9193,9522,"Oh. I'm glad you're using protection."],[9593,9664,"Dad?"],[9793,9848,"Could you never"],[9848,9977,"say that again, please?"]],"5":[[929,1054,"I owed him a call."],[1338,1421,"Last night I,"],[1442,1564,"I promised I'd call him,"],[1630,1693,"but..."],[2669,2773,"They're gonna come now."],[2923,3002,"All of them."],[3123,3211,"Maybe do Mum a favor"],[3211,3323,"and wear some knickers."],[3482,3628,"Mum can piss off."],[3836,3966,"Maybe do Dad a favor then."],[4220,4366,"It's good to see you, Len."],[4562,4679,"Robert loved you most."],[5083,5154,"Hey."],[5417,5567,"This sucks, huh?"],[6919,7094,"Oh, no!"],[7411,7511,"Oh, my God."],[7511,7682,"I'm never flying commercial again."],[7699,7803,"Where's our plane?"],[7803,7911,"Oh, god. It's redic."],[7920,8011,"It's recock."],[8070,8308,"Saw your fanny on the front page, Len."],[8308,8403,"Well done, you."],[8403,8512,"Yeah, but how many people"],[8512,8662,"even read the tabs, anyway?"],[8662,8750,"Like, three million?"],[8804,8900,"I mean, that's less than what's seen"],[8900,8992,"your bits anyway."],[9229,9350,"Yadda, yadda. Whatever."],[9717,9834,"Oh, God..."],[9834,9934,"Sorry about Bobby."],[9934,10147,"Yeah. Like, no fair."],[10556,10668,"So, is our father about?"],[10668,10818,"That neglectful tosser."]],"6":[[241,374,"Marcus said you wanted to see me?"],[608,700,"Please, be sit."],[833,933,"How do you like your tea?"],[996,1142,"I like it when it's called coffee."],[1184,1313,"Iced dirty chai with soy."],[1384,1484,"I know those are words, but I"],[1484,1592,"have no idea what they mean."],[1976,2101,"Last year when my mom died,"],[2210,2310,"people didn't really know what"],[2310,2410,"to say or do."],[2510,2572,"But it was always nice"],[2572,2668,"when they tried."],[2839,2985,"I just wanted to say that I'm sorry"],[2985,3081,"about Robert."],[3144,3311,"He seemed like a wonderful person."],[3427,3511,"He was."],[3778,3870,"Things will be a bit mad around"],[3870,3978,"here now, so..."],[4041,4166,"I just wanted to say,"],[4182,4303,"about last night, it was um..."],[4303,4341,"It's fine."],[4408,4529,"I didn't know who you were."],[4595,4708,"When Marcus recognized you"],[4708,4812,"I realized it was you..."],[4812,4871,"It's okay."],[4971,5112,"I didn't know who you were either."],[5375,5459,"That’s not even funny."],[5600,5734,"I haven't been back that long,"],[5734,5826,"and even though we live"],[5826,5926,"in the same palace,"],[5988,6063,"it doesn't mean we live"],[6063,6164,"in the same world."],[6289,6380,"Besides, my dad would"],[6380,6531,"prefer to keep things quiet."],[6747,6860,"Was he upset when he found out?"],[7048,7135,"A little."],[7227,7352,"But I knew what I was doing."],[7498,7565,"Does the Queen know?"],[7836,7961,"The Queen knows everything."]],"7":[[2998,3219,"Helena. Don't go."],[3557,3661,"When a mother loses"],[3661,3819,"her first-born son..."],[4195,4374,"I believe she's allowed to grieve."],[4583,4741,"Not when she's the Queen."],[5663,5842,"And so the world gathers"],[5842,5967,"to pay their respects"],[5967,6180,"and say goodbye to Prince Robert,"],[6218,6451,"taken suddenly and far too soon"],[6451,6576,"at the age of 23."],[6689,6922,"Charismatic. Compassionate."],[6922,7160,"Robert was Britain's beloved son,"],[7177,7373,"and he, like all the Royals,"],[7394,7644,"loved the people with all his heart."],[7644,7840,"God, how I loathe those people."],[7919,8145,"Draped in their football jerseys"],[8145,8290,"and false sentiments."],[8395,8478,"One can practically"],[8478,8591,"smell them from here."],[8787,8995,"I would've thought you'd be happy,"],[8995,9100,"dear Uncle."],[9133,9233,"I mean, after all, you're one"],[9233,9404,"step closer to the throne."],[9479,9583,"All you have to do is wait"],[9583,9692,"for your brother to die"],[9692,9813,"and then kill Liam."],[9967,10205,"Oh, and kill me too, of course."],[10259,10388,"The drugs will do that."],[10447,10584,"And if not, the syphilis"],[10584,10680,"will drive you mad"],[10680,10906,"and they'll declare you unfit to rule."],[11010,11248,"Either way, win win."],[11277,11439,"Speaking of syphilis..."],[11518,11673,"you probably should've had that"],[11673,11877,"whore of an ex-wife of yours checked"],[11960,12156,"before those two were born."],[12636,12899,"What's that smell? Is that your feet?"],[12993,13124,"I thought it was your fanny."],[13137,13295,"It well could be in this boiler."]],"8":[[212,287,"Hey."],[462,571,"You just tryin’ to get away from me?"],[662,779,"I'm sorry, I didn't..."],[946,1046,"I was trying to be respectful."],[1305,1392,"They wrote a speech for me"],[1463,1555,"to give to the press."],[1693,1935,"\"We lost more than a man or a Prince."],[1989,2106,"We lost a beacon."],[2164,2285,"The kind on which a nation"],[2285,2485,"relies to confer legitimacy"],[2514,2669,"and create unity.\""],[2794,2869,"My brother dies and"],[2869,2990,"they script my feelings."],[3182,3265,"Well, no matter what,"],[3290,3436,"I know he'll be proud of you today."],[3678,3749,"Hey."],[3970,4087,"Let's have dinner some time."],[4233,4350,"Are you asking me out before"],[4350,4425,"your brother's funeral?"],[4454,4541,"It's my first non-scripted"],[4541,4629,"moment of the day."],[4783,4854,"I like it."],[4896,5029,"You should go off script more often."],[5138,5200,"Good luck."],[5200,5280,"Thank you."],[5667,6001,"Really? Poor Gemma."],[6039,6218,"Poor Gemma broke up with me, Mum."],[6251,6364,"Well, can you blame her?"],[6439,6627,"Might I remind you the entire world"],[6627,6802,"will be watching you today?"],[6881,7036,"You’ll give your quote to Fiona,"],[7036,7161,"you'll acknowledge the crowd,"],[7161,7311,"and you'll escort me to the car."],[7428,7536,"And try not to sleep with"],[7536,7665,"anyone on the way."]],"9":[[4923,5035,"Prince Liam,"],[5061,5219,"with heavy hearts we offer"],[5219,5328,"our condolences to you"],[5328,5440,"as a grieving nation."],[5832,5891,"One of the great things"],[5891,6003,"about my brother was..."],[6149,6316,"he wasn't afraid to be his own man."],[6500,6579,"I'll miss him."],[7743,8047,"My God. You wretched brats."],[8047,8214,"Your brother, my first-born son,"],[8214,8397,"and you can't find the decorum,"],[8397,8485,"the civility,"],[8485,8589,"to honor his memory."],[8606,8698,"What is wrong with you?"],[8727,8902,"Was that scripted too?"],[8940,9077,"We script you because we can't"],[9077,9252,"trust either of you to come up with a"],[9252,9386,"reasonably coherent thought."],[9503,9669,"You know, God forbid"],[9695,9866,"we appear incoherent"],[9866,10011,"when our brother dies."],[10041,10149,"Or sad."],[10220,10383,"You might try it, Queen."],[10449,10587,"You are a little bitch."],[10750,10858,"I'm inconsolable."],[10900,10962,"Really?"],[11038,11196,"Because our dad is out there genuinely"],[11196,11321,"grieving over the death of his son,"],[11375,11488,"while you're in here worrying"],[11488,11584,"about the family's image"],[11584,11730,"and topping off on the Botox."]],"10":[[1,64,"At least I'm not"],[64,180,"slumming with the help."],[318,477,"And she's so plain."],[610,756,"I think Richard III had it right."],[773,873,"Lock the kids in the tower"],[927,1015,"and be done with them."],[1052,1176,"Maybe Henry VIII had it right."],[1238,1366,"He just killed his wives."],[1557,1615,"One of them because"],[1615,1724,"she looked fat."],[1899,2057,"They always take the good ones."],[2174,2287,"How did Robert die?"],[2320,2404,"All they'll tell us is that"],[2404,2504,"it was a military accident."],[2570,2679,"That's all you need to know."],[2679,2837,"Whatever it was..."],[2937,3046,"good for him."],[3154,3279,"If you ask me, Robert"],[3279,3363,"was the lucky one."],[7050,7154,"I was thinking of taking some time"],[7154,7242,"off from school."],[7300,7421,"Check up on Robert's charities."],[7446,7492,"I would have thought"],[7492,7559,"your studies would be"],[7559,7671,"a welcome distraction."],[7826,7905,"Speaking of"],[7905,8046,"welcome distractions..."],[8397,8551,"I asked a guest to join us."],[9078,9366,"Mum, Dad, this is Ophelia."]],"11":[[9,343,"Ophelia Pryce, artist in residence."],[455,589,"For His Majesty's Silver Jubilee,"],[589,743,"I presented him with a very"],[743,833,"serious work of art."],[877,993,"I can recall, you were"],[993,1123,"working in the paste"],[1148,1356,"and yarn medium at the time."],[1465,1619,"I retired shortly thereafter."],[1694,1798,"What's your focus now?"],[1832,1994,"Art History at Churchill."],[2044,2182,"Ophelia's doing a joint honors degree."],[2220,2315,"Art History and Dance."],[2345,2478,"Which is grand news, indeed,"],[2537,2687,"as the Prime Minister himself"],[2728,2858,"recently expressed a concern"],[2858,2937,"about the shortage"],[2937,3133,"of frolicking art historians."],[3191,3383,"I'm sure you'll be twerking your way"],[3383,3483,"to a great future."],[3508,3683,"Well, she is dining with the"],[3683,3817,"future King of England,"],[3817,4013,"so she's got that going for her."],[4067,4226,"It's good that you're here, Ophelia."],[4284,4393,"You can give us the common"],[4393,4476,"point of view."],[4493,4651,"How is the public faring"],[4651,4818,"in the wake of Robert's death?"],[4931,5035,"I think we'll go."],[5068,5181,"Robert carried himself"],[5181,5273,"with a nobility and"],[5273,5435,"grace that was easy to admire."],[5498,5698,"He was inspiring and he was ours."],[5852,5948,"But I can only speak from"],[5948,6107,"this commoner's perspective."],[6173,6307,"You say he was yours,"],[6395,6499,"but you're American."],[6520,6678,"My mom was American, but I was"],[6678,6866,"born here and raised in the States"],[6866,6945,"because it was..."],[6945,7070,"Because it was safer."],[7291,7371,"Please, stay."],[7529,7713,"I appreciate your kind words"],[7729,7942,"about Robert, Ophelia. I do."],[8080,8180,"Robert joined the military"],[8180,8246,"because I did."],[8301,8467,"Like my father before me"],[8467,8601,"and his father before him"],[8601,8672,"and so on."],[8747,8880,"Robert was killed by tradition."],[8880,9051,"He died a hero's death."],[9076,9164,"A noble death."],[9164,9310,"Which merely means he's dead."],[9310,9377,"Why?"],[9414,9564,"I seem to have lost my appetite."],[9598,9735,"I think you'll want to stay to hear"],[9735,9877,"this next part, my love."],[9994,10102,"I think you all will."],[10169,10315,"So put away your phones"],[10315,10382,"and your drugs"],[10382,10545,"and your lust for the server's sponge"],[10545,10649,"and pay attention."],[10707,10795,"I'm considering"],[10795,10907,"asking Parliament"],[10949,11032,"for a referendum."],[11241,11370,"To abolish the Monarchy."]],"12":[[833,979,"What does that mean exactly?"],[1100,1300,"That means you'll have to get a job."],[1300,1534,"A vote, idiot of my loins,"],[1534,1675,"to eradicate us."],[1738,1842,"To erase us."],[1871,2055,"Yeah, but who votes?"],[2055,2138,"The people."],[2205,2289,"But they can't do that."],[2289,2493,"I mean, they're the people."],[2530,2747,"You know, and we're, like, \"us\"."],[2747,2952,"They can and they have."],[3043,3202,"Ever heard of America?"],[3202,3252,"Oh."],[3315,3632,"But... I do not want to be American."],[3719,3819,"I do not want to walk around"],[3819,3965,"like Justin Bieber"],[3965,4078,"with no shirt on and"],[4078,4165,"my trousers hanging off."],[4207,4307,"He's Canadian."],[4324,4399,"Even worse."],[4537,4637,"They can't make us Canadian,"],[4637,4703,"can they, Daddy?"],[4716,4841,"Canadian and poor"],[4841,4966,"just like Justin Bieber?"],[5008,5091,"The British Monarchy"],[5091,5337,"always has been and always will be."],[5337,5550,"\"Always will be\" killed Robert."],[5946,6117,"The people need the Monarchy."],[6126,6505,"The people need bread and jobs"],[6543,6680,"and a decent wage."],[6810,6876,"They don't need us."],[6902,7189,"With all due respect, my King..."],[7302,7406,"how would you know?"],[7890,7948,"Truman."],[8103,8165,"Your Majesty?"],[8315,8424,"I need a favor."],[8641,8778,"I know you're tired..."],[8895,9070,"and despondent over Robert."],[9175,9250,"But, honestly,"],[9321,9429,"it was out of character for you to"],[9429,9600,"speak so carelessly about the family."],[9729,9955,"Referendums and Parliament"],[9955,10142,"and disbanding the Monarchy."],[10167,10272,"It's all so dramatic."],[10347,10543,"And, frankly, it's weak,"],[10593,10735,"and less than who you are."],[10855,11018,"Forgive me, Your Majesty... I was..."],[11377,11573,"My God, it's good to be the King."]],"13":[[1093,1172,"I understand you've had"],[1172,1289,"dinner with the Prince."],[1481,1706,"He invited me. I said yes."],[1706,1815,"Next time say no."],[1898,1977,"Do you ever think maybe"],[1977,2086,"I said yes for you?"],[2127,2223,"That saying no might"],[2223,2319,"make it awkward"],[2319,2419,"between you and the King?"],[2444,2494,"Did you?"],[2628,2670,"No."],[2745,2891,"I said yes because I wanted to go."],[2949,3024,"But speaking of places"],[3024,3108,"we've gone lately,"],[3149,3241,"did you visit Mom's grave?"],[3287,3358,"I've been working."],[3395,3558,"The King's welfare is never ending."],[3587,3629,"Yeah."],[3671,3787,"If you've got something to say,"],[3787,3842,"say it."],[4017,4200,"You know what? Fine. I will."],[4275,4400,"Two things, actually."],[4459,4580,"I appreciate that you"],[4580,4751,"worry about me, and I get it."],[4776,4905,"Being close to the Royal Family"],[4905,4989,"is what got Mom killed"],[4989,5093,"and that's where you go"],[5093,5160,"when I'm near them."],[5247,5427,"But it's not the same thing, Dad."],[5435,5539,"It is the same thing."],[5539,5685,"And frankly, it's not fair to me."],[5706,5814,"Because you worry about me,"],[5814,5889,"when I'm near them."],[5902,6048,"It's dangerous, Ophelia."],[6048,6165,"Even for a moment."],[6736,6803,"Do you know how many"],[6803,6982,"steps it takes to get from the elevator"],[6982,7112,"to the chair you're sitting in?"],[7262,7324,"Seven."],[7466,7508,"Do you know how many"],[7508,7591,"to your bedroom?"],[7650,7729,"23."],[7875,8008,"I lie awake at night"],[8050,8200,"and wait to count those steps."],[8200,8284,"Because at least I know"],[8284,8450,"you're home and you're safe."],[8630,8797,"You worry about a moment."],[8943,9139,"I worry about all the other moments."],[9301,9355,"Hey."],[9689,9835,"You said there were two things."],[10653,10899,"She always put us first, you know?"],[11153,11270,"You didn't visit her grave."],[11337,11528,"You haven't taken a single day off"],[11528,11629,"since she died."],[11875,12012,"That's screwed up, Dad."],[12342,12434,"Mom deserves better."]],"14":[[824,953,"Oh, look who it is."],[953,1128,"Slag One and Slag Two."],[1241,1416,"Get in here, you daft bitches."],[1787,2258,"I will take... this and this..."],[2375,2638,"I'll leave you with this, okay?"],[2638,2792,"God forbid we get"],[2792,2934,"any more of the likes of you."],[3067,3209,"Oh, yeah, Penelope doesn't"],[3209,3314,"actually get high."],[3359,3489,"Yeah, she says it makes her queasy."],[3530,3756,"She is also a virgin."],[3918,4052,"Just a vaggy virgin."],[4085,4194,"Not a blowy or a handy."],[4223,4365,"Now I'm queasy."],[4481,4607,"Well, you're getting high tonight."],[4644,4702,"Both of you."],[4757,4853,"Just not here."],[5645,5720,"Yes!"],[5929,6096,"Maybe... maybe you'll be"],[6096,6221,"better at shagging."],[6317,6421,"Although I doubt it."],[6621,6834,"I can't believe Robert's gone."],[6959,7222,"He would've been a stellar King, yeah?"],[7234,7305,"If there's even going to"],[7305,7426,"be another King."],[7514,7614,"Can you imagine it?"],[7743,7893,"And not being a princess?"],[8047,8273,"I'm just not qualified to do anything else."],[8310,8469,"I think I can do all kinds of things."],[8469,8711,"Yeah, like serve tea at the Ritz."],[8748,8886,"Yeah, you know, like, oh..."],[8919,9032,"\"Would you like another"],[9032,9157,"pot of tea, ladies"],[9186,9324,"with some finger cakes?\""],[9324,9382,"Food."],[9382,9520,"\"Perhaps like a sweet...\""],[9541,9641,"I'm starving."],[10004,10133,"I can't feel my legs."],[10396,10517,"I need assistance."],[10713,10779,"Len?"],[10892,10980,"Help!"]],"15":[[82,166,"Come in."],[754,933,"His Royal Highness asked for me?"],[933,1017,"Yes."],[1096,1188,"Regrettably, there have been"],[1188,1367,"complaints about your efforts."],[1425,1559,"Enthusiasm of service,"],[1559,1667,"that sort of thing."],[1705,1805,"I can assure you this is"],[1805,1938,"the first I'm hearing of it."],[1980,2072,"I'll do better."],[2143,2280,"I can't be on benefits."],[2280,2351,"Of course."],[2385,2560,"You seem terribly nervous."],[2652,2818,"Am I that intimidating?"],[2864,2948,"It's just..."],[3140,3269,"Well, I've heard things."],[3269,3323,"Oh?"],[3390,3711,"What sort of things?"],[3961,4132,"That some of the women"],[4132,4353,"have had to do things"],[4353,4470,"to keep their jobs."],[4674,4724,"With you."],[4754,4875,"You've heard that they had to"],[4875,5004,"have sex with me?"],[5091,5242,"Well, I can assure you that's"],[5242,5363,"not the case."],[5438,5592,"Nor was it my intention"],[5592,5692,"when I asked you here."],[5738,5951,"So, please, relax."],[6176,6493,"I'm... simply looking for"],[6493,6777,"a token display of dedication."],[6956,7093,"In a service capacity."],[7177,7427,"Besides, even the President"],[7427,7552,"of the United States"],[7552,7715,"said it wasn't sex."],[8633,8960,"And remember, enthusiasm counts."]],"16":[[635,923,"Is that the King of England"],[923,1057,"skulking about?"],[1323,1407,"Fancy some?"],[1490,1574,"This was reserved for the"],[1574,1753,"Prime Minister but..."],[1845,1991,"that fat bastard does not"],[1991,2124,"need any more pie."],[2237,2383,"I could always sell pastries."],[2425,2537,"You know, if you decide to"],[2537,2641,"disband the Monarchy."],[2679,2908,"Which I am all for, by the way."],[2917,3084,"Something tells me your opinion"],[3084,3196,"is in the minority."],[3230,3392,"And when has that mattered?"],[3505,3663,"You trust your instincts."],[3734,3813,"You follow your heart."],[3813,3989,"That's what makes you great."],[4151,4268,"A great King."],[4472,4685,"And a kind of okay father."],[5202,5273,"How are you, Lenny?"],[5423,5465,"Um..."],[5582,5661,"I'm sad."],[5786,6078,"But I'm baked out of my mind..."],[6166,6308,"So right now I'm well."],[6499,6600,"They worry about you."],[6708,6892,"Your mother. Liam."],[6967,7058,"Not you?"],[7192,7263,"Not so much."],[7296,7484,"Oh, thanks a lot!"],[7884,7934,"Go to bed."],[8139,8230,"Do better tomorrow."],[8522,8743,"I'm the King. You have to do as I say."],[9394,9444,"Dad?"],[9932,10061,"Do I disappoint you?"],[10291,10466,"Those qualities you say"],[10466,10566,"make me great..."],[10816,10996,"I see them in you every day."],[11279,11488,"Don't medicate all that wonder."],[11780,11867,"Your brother loved you"],[11867,11984,"with all his heart."],[12297,12385,"So do I."],[12564,12639,"Yeah."]],"17":[[1744,1931,"Let me recap my week for you."],[2299,2411,"My daughter's vagina"],[2411,2590,"was on the cover of no less"],[2590,2741,"than four tabloids."],[2937,3095,"My firstborn child was killed."],[3341,3433,"My husband announced he"],[3433,3562,"wants to abolish the only life"],[3562,3650,"I've ever known."],[3771,3883,"And his footman"],[3883,4034,"nearly saw my snatch."],[4138,4250,"I miss him."],[4592,4705,"With every breath."],[4822,4939,"And what tears at me is"],[4939,5051,"the knowledge that he could have"],[5051,5193,"been anything in the world."],[5593,5744,"I'll not lose another son or"],[5744,5856,"daughter to this."],[5915,6052,"They're my children, too."],[6278,6365,"They're no worse than any other"],[6365,6469,"kids their age."],[6557,6732,"Your daughter was \"rolling balls\""],[6732,6882,"in the state dining room."],[7053,7195,"Now she's stoned and eating"],[7195,7366,"the Prime Minister's pie."],[7470,7716,"I'm not sure that ending this"],[7716,7867,"will heal any of us..."],[8042,8150,"but staying the same"],[8150,8267,"will destroy us."],[8651,8901,"The English Crown has been protected"],[8901,9176,"and defended for thousands of years."],[9176,9314,"From clans with sticks"],[9314,9418,"through World Wars,"],[9418,9577,"legions of lives lost..."],[9577,9718,"But not this one."],[10073,10186,"Not our son."],[10269,10519,"You are the King of England,"],[10569,10632,"goddammit."],[10715,10870,"Act like it."],[11074,11291,"That's exactly what I intend to do."],[12884,13072,"Okay, so we'll be off now."],[13072,13314,"I guess our father's not..."],[13464,13568,"Shut up!"],[13589,13681,"If this were Asia we could eat you"],[13681,13768,"with mushy peas."],[13818,13964,"Water."],[14031,14110,"For dear God do not"],[14110,14215,"slam the bloody door!"],[14223,14302,"Stop shouting!"],[14302,14457,"I'll shout if I bloody want to!"],[14457,14636,"Your breath, it smells like a fart."]],"18":[[167,388,"Hey. You okay?"],[1456,1526,"You're probably wondering"],[1526,1627,"why I wanted to see you."],[1685,1806,"Something to do with Liam?"],[1869,1977,"His Royal Highness,"],[1977,2090,"Prince Liam."],[2102,2266,"Right. Sorry."],[2387,2499,"My son likes you."],[2607,2836,"But... I would be very happy"],[2836,3028,"if you'd discourage the relationship."],[3136,3274,"It's not really a relationship."],[3307,3416,"No, of course, it's not."],[3624,3804,"Is your father still a workaholic?"],[3946,4054,"He loves his job."],[4112,4200,"Some people feel as though"],[4200,4292,"he's getting a little old"],[4292,4404,"for his line of work,"],[4404,4554,"but, of course, I would never"],[4554,4688,"allow him to be replaced,"],[4713,4801,"considering the favor"],[4801,4926,"you'd be doing for me."],[5243,5339,"May I speak freely?"],[5389,5439,"Of course."],[5468,5626,"Okay. Well, the thing is,"],[5689,5777,"I wasn't even planning on"],[5777,5885,"seeing your son again."],[5956,6156,"At least until you insisted on girl talk"],[6156,6227,"and started threatening"],[6227,6302,"my father."],[6377,6536,"Maybe don't speak quite so freely."],[6669,6778,"You're the Queen Of England."],[6786,6861,"I get it."],[6940,7107,"But your son is your problem, not mine."],[7203,7311,"Be careful, little girl."],[7424,7591,"As you say, I am the Queen of England,"],[7591,7774,"and this is my house."],[8016,8125,"Perhaps if you still had a mother,"],[8125,8246,"you'd have better manners."],[8563,8688,"I'm not afraid of you."],[8729,8813,"Afraid of me?"],[8896,9034,"Of course you're not."],[9134,9234,"Why would you be?"],[9618,9931,"Now... curtsy to your Queen"],[9964,10072,"and walk away."],[10231,10414,"I would, but my mother"],[10414,10549,"never taught me how."]],"19":[[471,613,"You know what really sucks, Marcus?"],[697,826,"Other than my brother dying?"],[951,1064,"You never drink with me."],[1139,1231,"I'm working, sir."],[1231,1314,"And stop calling me sir."],[1314,1472,"You've been my security detail for..."],[1472,1539,"Six years."],[1539,1698,"Six years."],[1769,1923,"Have a drink, you pussy."],[2186,2315,"\"Uneasy lies the head that"],[2315,2457,"wears a crown, sir.\""],[2569,2778,"Shakespeare. Henry IV."],[2807,2886,"Yeah, I know it's Shakespeare,"],[2886,2953,"Irish prick."],[2953,3003,"Careful."],[3112,3258,"You know, your name is Irish."],[3328,3412,"So look at it this way."],[3412,3616,"Maybe you’re illegitimate."],[3691,3783,"And in that case, you can't"],[3783,3866,"be King anyway."],[3912,3992,"Did you just say..."],[4008,4104,"That your mother, the Queen,"],[4104,4221,"got owned by an Irishman?"],[4242,4405,"Yes, that's what I implied,"],[4405,4559,"you potentially Irish bastard."],[4947,5076,"Talk to me about Ophelia, Marcus."],[5251,5330,"Ophelia, sir?"],[5372,5401,"Ophelia,"],[5401,5547,"You recognized her in my dorm room."],[5614,5668,"Right."],[5706,5748,"Well..."],[5835,6056,"Ophelia is Ted's daughter."],[6081,6215,"And Ted's my boss."],[6340,6623,"So... confidentially..."],[6732,7195,"Ophelia is my boss's daughter, sir."],[7403,7612,"Marcus, don't they give you"],[7612,7691,"diplomacy lessons"],[7691,7845,"before you become the King's security?"],[7904,7991,"They do indeed, sir."],[8004,8108,"Well, you suck at it."],[8179,8275,"You think Eleanor's security detail"],[8275,8383,"is like this?"],[8450,8671,"Eleanor's security detail was fired, sir."],[9451,9522,"Enjoy that?"]],"20":[[276,443,"Oh, perhaps I could call the Keeper"],[443,581,"of The Cellar, Your Majesty."],[639,831,"Okay, It's \"Deputy Yeoman"],[831,939,"of the Royal Cellars\","],[939,1089,"and I'm \"Your Highness\"."],[1089,1202,"If you're going to work here,"],[1202,1344,"you better learn the language."],[1344,1502,"Oh. Apologies, Your Highness."],[1548,1657,"Are you nervous?"],[1736,1899,"Very much so, yes."],[1899,2090,"Why? Because I'm the Princess"],[2090,2291,"or because I'm hot?"],[2291,2445,"Well, no, because you're the Princess."],[2724,3025,"Because you're hot. Uh... both."],[3046,3162,"Inappropriate."],[3179,3317,"Apologies, Your Highness."],[3425,3604,"I'm so messing with you."],[3650,3972,"Though I do have serious concerns"],[3972,4092,"about your ability to guard"],[4092,4251,"my body, Jasper."],[4314,4443,"The good news for you is"],[4443,4593,"that I can look after myself."],[4639,4839,"Now, here, hold out your arms."],[5052,5227,"Okay. You look concerned."],[5227,5385,"There are 25,000 bottles"],[5385,5540,"of wine down here, Jasper."],[5590,5965,"I'm the Princess. My house. My wine!"],[5965,6028,"Okay?"],[6028,6203,"Oh, no. No, of course. Yes."],[6220,6353,"But, look, if the Deputy Yeoman"],[6353,6553,"sees you, you're an alcoholic burglar."],[6582,6649,"Got it?"],[6733,6820,"Oooh."],[6941,7154,"This is a 1942 something"],[7154,7233,"or other."],[7287,7446,"After I drink this, I'll need you to find a"],[7446,7688,"really good spot to hide the evidence."],[7688,7788,"Sorry. You just said..."],[7788,7888,"Okay. You can go."],[7913,8105,"But tomorrow night we're going out,"],[8105,8217,"so could you lighten up?"],[8259,8551,"Yes, Your Majest... Highness."],[8551,8601,"Okay."],[8676,8780,"Right."],[9948,10249,"Phe! Stay and drink with me."],[10503,10674,"You look like you could use one."],[10799,11012,"Yeah, I could definitely use one."],[11033,11220,"1942, it is."],[11650,12067,"Some for you and... more for me."],[12267,12463,"To Robert."],[12463,12734,"And to the fading days"],[12734,12885,"of a crumbling empire."],[13806,13973,"So... How are things"],[13973,14107,"with the new boyfriend?"],[14173,14282,"It wasn't like that."],[14361,14507,"I tried to explain that to your mother."],[14603,14832,"And did she threaten you and"],[14832,14999,"tell you to never see him again?"],[15095,15199,"Pretty much."],[15370,15471,"But it was just a hook-up."],[15541,15700,"I wasn't looking for a boyfriend."]],"21":[[276,401,"So much for dating a guy"],[401,585,"for his money and power."],[718,994,"Art, planes, boats, land."],[1039,1235,"A couple of castles, the Crown Jewels,"],[1235,1448,"and diplomatic immunity."],[1582,1799,"But, you know, the kid's terrible-looking"],[1799,1911,"so I can see why none of that"],[1911,2032,"would matter."],[2637,2762,"I'm sorry about Robert."],[2866,2941,"Yeah."],[3246,3350,"I'm sorry about your mum."],[3475,3563,"You knew my mother?"],[3684,3826,"From a distance."],[3926,4038,"She was elegant, your mum."],[4243,4343,"And your poor father,"],[4343,4464,"he was so tortured."],[4555,4647,"I guess so."],[4781,4893,"I know so."],[5277,5398,"You know, when I quit"],[5398,5548,"university last year,"],[5623,5915,"I used to kick about, and try and"],[5915,6032,"go unrecognized."],[6032,6307,"And mostly I'd end up in this park"],[6307,6474,"stealing things from homeless people."],[6683,6958,"Anyway, I would see your dad there."],[7095,7358,"And he would sit on this bench..."],[7442,7588,"It was always the same bench..."],[7838,8063,"..and he would just weep."],[8242,8472,"You know, like he was gutted inside."],[8672,8806,"Are you sure that was my father?"],[8981,9102,"He had this book."],[9227,9369,"\"All Creatures Great And Small\"?"],[9510,9619,"It's how he met my mom."],[9736,9807,"She was reading that book"],[9807,9890,"in the park"],[9986,10082,"and they had a chat about it."],[10153,10432,"So, anyway, this went on for weeks."],[10432,10737,"And... eventually my mother"],[10737,10845,"summoned him"],[10845,10941,"and told him"],[10941,11054,"enough was enough."],[11204,11291,"Do you know what he did?"],[11391,11462,"Your dad?"]],"22":[[23,411,"He looked her... right in the eyes..."],[473,824,"..his boss, the Queen of England..."],[895,1299,"..and he said, \"Sack me or deal with it."],[1445,1650,"My wife deserves a lifetime of tears,"],[1650,1787,"and not even the Queen will decide"],[1787,1912,"when enough is enough.\""],[2221,2384,"Your dad's a bad-ass."],[2475,2575,"Everyone knows it."],[2792,2913,"Everyone except me."],[3159,3247,"I gotta go."],[3481,3522,"Hey."],[3677,3760,"Thank you."],[3839,3960,"You're a bad-ass too."],[4586,4628,"No."],[4719,4911,"I'm just a bitch with money and power."],[5128,5249,"But I do make it look good."],[5929,6041,"You were out late."],[6400,6650,"Hey. What's all this about?"],[6784,6930,"I just wanna say that I love you."],[6946,7055,"Because I do."],[7852,7943,"Good night, Dad."],[9411,9457,"What?"],[9499,9549,"Are you gonna tell me why"],[9549,9658,"the Queen was standing in"],[9658,9778,"my living room or am I meant"],[9778,9920,"to pretend it never happened?"],[9995,10125,"She just wanted to hang out."],[10125,10221,"We're kind of besties,"],[10221,10300,"me and the Queen."],[10734,10909,"She wanted to tell me not to see Liam."],[10942,11113,"She also threatened you,"],[11113,11267,"took a cheap shot at Mom, and"],[11267,11426,"was pretty much a complete bitch."],[11505,11601,"And before you say anything,"],[11601,11764,"I wanna say that I'm sorry."],[11789,11872,"Again."],[11956,12081,"A girl has a few gin and tonics"],[12081,12202,"and all hell breaks loose."],[12264,12381,"Do you want to see Liam?"],[12523,12719,"Dad, there's no seeing. Okay?"],[12790,12986,"We hang out. And no, I wasn't"],[12986,13057,"planning on it."],[13086,13161,"Good. Because I agree"],[13161,13211,"with the Queen."],[13211,13295,"I think it's for the best."],[13390,13507,"But if you change your mind,"],[13591,13732,"don't, for a second, worry about me,"],[13732,13808,"or my job,"],[13808,13891,"or what the Queen wants,"],[13891,14004,"or any of it. Okay?"],[14083,14145,"Really?"],[14262,14371,"She might rule a nation, but"],[14371,14546,"that icy bitch has no hold on"],[14546,14663,"my daughter's heart."],[14792,14867,"Besides..."],[14975,15038,"they've taken enough"],[15038,15134,"from us already."],[15447,15509,"Thanks, Dad."]],"23":[[262,421,"Well, you might not want to hang out with him"],[421,558,"with him but he certainly seems to"],[558,763,"want to hang out with you."],[779,867,"Next King of England"],[867,954,"on his way up."],[1809,1876,"Good morning, sir."],[1876,1951,"Good morning, Ted."],[2047,2093,"Hi."],[2247,2339,"Oh, hey."],[2402,2464,"What's up?"],[2523,2648,"Sorry to come unannounced."],[2723,2827,"That's what she said."],[2931,3002,"Wow."],[3202,3461,"So, Eleanor said you and my mum"],[3461,3607,"are hanging out now."],[3653,3874,"Yeah. We go to the mall together,"],[3874,3995,"trade clothes,"],[3995,4099,"threaten each other."],[4099,4187,"I should have warned you."],[4187,4299,"It's kind of what we do."],[4333,4479,"I meet someone, she threatens them."],[4562,4716,"It passes for love in our family."],[4767,4967,"It's fine. I mean, it's"],[4967,5038,"nice of you to stop by,"],[5038,5192,"but totally unnecessary."],[5200,5375,"Good, because that's not why"],[5375,5459,"I stopped by."],[5667,5751,"I was wondering if you wanted"],[5751,5863,"to grab a coffee some time."],[5926,6014,"Uh, but..."],[6014,6226,"What’s that sludge that you drink?"],[6256,6581,"Iced soy dirty... girl?"],[6581,6752,"Iced dirty chai with soy."],[6789,7035,"It's delicious. You should try it."],[7035,7273,"I plan to. With you if you say yes."],[7394,7469,"I don't know."],[7528,7644,"It's just coffee, Ophelia."],[7649,7890,"If that's your story."],[8149,8303,"Fine. Coffee."],[8328,8391,"You and me."],[8412,8595,"Me and the future King of England,"],[8595,8758,"having all the coffee."],[8787,8992,"Good. Um... yeah."],[8992,9321,"A little awkward, but I'm still in."],[9563,9642,"I'll text you."],[9676,9738,"Okay."],[9738,9855,"I've gotta go."],[10443,10681,"Hey. Thanks for stopping by."],[10789,10864,"I wanted to."],[10960,11064,"Had nothing to do with the Queen."],[11728,11924,"This is gonna suck."]],"24":[[322,414,"Hey, Robby."],[694,790,"I miss you..."],[995,1141,"..and I'm gonna miss you."],[1516,1683,"I'll be fine. You know me."],[1958,2087,"Look out for Liam, though."],[2479,2655,"I think he's gonna need it."],[4144,4269,"Where to, Your Highness?"],[4598,4853,"Have you ever been to Paris, Jasper?"],[7789,7876,"Dad, are you considering"],[7876,7947,"abolishing the Monarchy"],[7947,8060,"because of me?"],[8106,8210,"Because you don't believe in me?"],[8544,8602,"No."],[8865,9003,"I'm considering it because"],[9003,9136,"I do believe in you."],[9232,9361,"And because I want something"],[9361,9449,"more for you."],[9749,9862,"What could be more than King?"],[9958,10054,"Love."],[10195,10446,"A family raised beyond the tabloids"],[10446,10596,"and the walls of a castle."],[10729,10963,"A life lived and not destined."]],"25":[[271,467,"I like Ophelia very much."],[626,699,"Me too."],[951,1026,"Her mother was killed"],[1026,1122,"because of me."],[1268,1423,"Because men always choose"],[1423,1544,"the wrong things."],[1644,1890,"They stalk power and wealth,"],[1956,2090,"and frivolous things they"],[2090,2228,"think will make them whole."],[2378,2490,"And it never does."],[2674,2791,"It never does."],[3141,3216,"But her father chose"],[3216,3329,"duty and honor"],[3379,3521,"and service to the King."],[3546,3692,"Those aren't frivolous things."],[3729,3812,"No."],[3963,4079,"If you asked him, could he"],[4079,4217,"do it all over again?"],[4250,4417,"What road do you think he'd travel?"],[4697,5026,"Ted chose duty over love."],[5181,5573,"Robert chose honor over his own path."],[5994,6123,"Choose love."],[6286,6457,"Choose your own path."],[6569,6786,"Those are the roads to travel, my son."],[7070,7145,"Come on."],[7917,8154,"Hey. Go home."],[8442,8646,"You are welcome."],[8701,8813,"Get out."],[9180,9368,"I apologize in advance, Jasper,"],[9368,9501,"for getting you sacked."],[9501,9731,"But... let's be honest, I mean,"],[9756,9864,"you were a dead man walking"],[9864,9948,"anyway."],[10077,10165,"Probably so."],[10402,10648,"What do you remember"],[10648,10744,"from last night, anyway?"],[10911,11011,"Umm..."],[11053,11224,"Nothing, Jasper."],[11224,11458,"You were perfectly forgettable."],[11645,11687,"It's just that"],[11687,11787,"I remember everything."],[11954,12146,"Yeah, well, like I said..."],[12208,12317,"You're very welcome."],[12329,12492,"See, I remember being at the club."],[12801,12930,"And I remember the drugs that"],[12930,13080,"I put in your drink."],[13360,13493,"And I remember every..."],[13597,13881,"sordid, depraved, self-loathing"],[13881,14039,"thing that you did after that."],[14369,14552,"You know, when I forget..."],[14761,14919,"I can always just watch the video."]],"26":[[6,181,"So I think I'll keep this job."],[648,807,"I like the benefits."],[2387,2513,"Hereditary power."],[2625,2775,"Entrenched privilege."],[2896,3101,"Can you really give all of this up?"],[3251,3568,"I can... and I will."],[3668,3972,"And do what? What would you do?"],[4022,4185,"Who would you be?"],[4302,4456,"No one's ever asked me that before."],[4915,5124,"I would like to have been a fisherman."],[5549,5678,"And, you, brother."],[5849,5970,"If you could have chosen"],[5970,6091,"your own destiny?"],[6245,6296,"If you could have been"],[6296,6396,"anything at all?"],[6683,6788,"What would you have been?"],[6950,7075,"King."],[9332,9474,"That was close, brother."],[10099,10274,"Long live the King."],[10591,10754,"You ready to get some tea?"],[10754,10846,"Coffee."],[10904,10971,"I gave it a shot."],[11205,11417,"Okay, here's the thing."],[11542,11680,"It might get a little crazy out there."],[11709,11914,"I'll be fine. It's just coffee."],[11943,12030,"If that's your story."],[12080,12310,"But just in case, I'm right here."]],"27":[[1539,1680,"My phone is password protected"],[1685,1772,"and your video is backed"],[1772,1910,"up onto several hard drives."],[2027,2081,"While you're here,"],[2081,2189,"good morning, baby..."],[2452,2619,"You can't do this to me."],[2673,2806,"You didn't seem to mind last night."],[2823,2965,"I meant blackmail."],[3053,3165,"You drugged me."],[3165,3286,"You drugged yourself."],[3349,3453,"You get blacked out all the time,"],[3453,3528,"and you know it."],[3624,3732,"Now go get me some breakfast."],[3895,3970,"What?"],[3999,4062,"You heard me."],[4183,4279,"Have you not been listening"],[4279,4421,"to me for the past two weeks?"],[4500,4637,"You don't order me around."],[4658,4846,"I order you. I'm the princess."],[4846,4963,"If by princess you mean"],[4963,5088,"potential porn star."],[5163,5384,"I'm famished from all this angry,"],[5384,5513,"supposed reluctant"],[5513,5626,"sex we've been having."],[5626,5818,"So, food. Now. Go."],[5864,5930,"No."],[6427,6652,"\"Dear Dethrowned...\""],[6861,6931,"You might want to"],[6931,7044,"put some clothes on."],[7115,7228,"Someone might film you"],[7228,7344,"and blackmail you with it."],[7344,7720,"I can't wait to ruin your life."],[7978,8103,"Go away."],[8112,8229,"It's the Queen of England."],[8295,8362,"Open the door."],[8429,8533,"You can't..."],[8979,9088,"What?"],[9196,9342,"Good morning, daughter"],[9342,9421,"who hates me."],[9663,9784,"It smells of sex in here."],[9830,9930,"Dirty sex."],[9984,10068,"Apparently someone's been"],[10093,10201,"beavering about."],[10264,10322,"What?"],[10356,10431,"Social media."],[10497,10589,"Did you say..."],[10648,10698,"\"Bored and horny, FML\"."],[10698,10881,"\"Bored and horny, FML\"."],[10915,11090,"For God's sake, what is FML?"],[11106,11353,"The f-word my life, Your Majesty."],[11386,11590,"\"This club sucks more d than me.\""],[11590,11815,"\"Dear Molly, get in my hole. Yum.\""],[11824,12124,"And then at 3:37am she signed off with"],[12195,12337,"\"My date is on fire,"],[12337,12533,"good thing my vagina is wet.\""],[12625,12771,"Honestly, Eleanor, who"],[12771,12908,"fondled you as a child?"],[12983,13188,"Uncle Cyrus, of course."],[13259,13384,"Why can't you drunk-text"],[13384,13480,"like a normal person?"],[13500,13605,"It's what I do, Your Majesty."],[13684,13842,"From now on, Rachel will be your"],[13842,14005,"social media advisor."],[14043,14268,"Whatever you post, Rachel will filter."],[14326,14439,"Not bloody likely."],[14489,14597,"Go on. Try it."],[15344,15619,"The queen can suck my..."]],"28":[[825,946,"\"I love my Mum!\"?"],[946,1088,"You can't do this."],[1146,1288,"Between you and..."],[1438,1676,"Fine. Just go."],[2135,2277,"\"I love my mum...\""],[2277,2473,"I love you too, darling."],[3495,3686,"Where's that breakfast?"],[3920,4041,"FML!"],[4128,4287,"Get me some coffee, too."],[4950,5171,"You know, I have to say, this dirty girl"],[5188,5517,"soy thing is almost as good as tea."],[5559,5680,"Well, considering it's the third time"],[5680,5809,"we've had \"all the coffee\","],[5830,5897,"I think you like it"],[5897,5976,"more than you like tea."],[6022,6181,"The coffee I endure."],[6226,6364,"It's the company I like."],[6418,6552,"Well played."],[6602,6802,"But I don't think the queen would agree."],[6831,6935,"The queen doesn't have to know."],[7065,7182,"I'm pretty sure she knows."],[8007,8116,"What is this?"],[8116,8224,"Those are the pistachio-encrusted"],[8224,8341,"eclairs, Your Majesty."],[8383,8500,"Eugh. No."],[8737,8896,"The King's head of security is"],[8896,9042,"to see you, Your Majesty."],[9092,9313,"Mm. These are divine."],[9317,9459,"If we could speak privately,"],[9459,9546,"My Queen."],[9555,9726,"I'm far too busy for that, Mr. Pryce."],[9734,9947,"I'm afraid I must insist."],[10026,10139,"Tell Hans the buttercake"],[10139,10255,"fingers and fruit tartlets"],[10255,10343,"are perfect,"],[10364,10431,"the pistachio thingies"],[10431,10514,"are a disaster."],[10539,10622,"Walk away."],[10698,10823,"You may stay, Lucius."],[10823,10944,"I'd prefer he didn't."],[11198,11361,"And I'd prefer it if your daughter"],[11361,11507,"weren't blowing my son."],[11523,11661,"We can't always get what we want,"],[11661,11749,"can we?"],[11857,12041,"We've received a series of threats."],[12041,12111,"Death threats?"],[12111,12207,"I’m afraid so."],[12207,12312,"Boring."],[12378,12479,"Let's discuss a legitimate"],[12479,12587,"threat to the monarchy."],[12637,12754,"Ophelia."],[12825,12975,"In regards to his Royal Highness,"],[12983,13137,"I gave her my blessing."],[13192,13300,"Well, I didn't."],[13542,13688,"Ask Rachel to change these."],[13688,13759,"Something with color."],[13801,13859,"Ma'am."],[13859,13988,"As far as threats are concerned,"],[13988,14164,"that's why we have you, isn't it?"],[14164,14293,"And if you're unable to adequately"],[14293,14414,"parent your daughter,"],[14414,14626,"the least you can do is not get us killed."],[14664,14831,"Enjoy the party, Mr. Pryce."]],"29":[[2,102,"What did he want?"],[122,176,"Oh."],[310,461,"Our daily death threat."],[461,536,"Boring."],[611,757,"Cyrus, you know how important"],[757,869,"this party is, don't you?"],[907,1036,"The battle for the monarchy"],[1036,1149,"starts today."],[1195,1324,"You can't wear plaid."],[1324,1441,"I'm not sure it matters."],[1441,1533,"Liam skipped the regent"],[1533,1633,"briefing again."],[1653,1708,"Did you fix it?"],[1720,1787,"Of course."],[1829,1916,"Good."],[2021,2187,"It's imperative we make Liam look"],[2187,2379,"every bit the worthy heir today."],[2388,2575,"It's the sole purpose of the party."],[2613,2755,"We make him look presentable and we"],[2755,2913,"influence a few important assets."],[2926,3130,"Speaking of, James Holloway"],[3130,3247,"also missed the meeting today."],[3255,3359,"He's influential."],[3359,3464,"Probably just as well."],[3464,3518,"Wouldn't you like to"],[3518,3597,"know where he was?"],[3664,3810,"Apparently he was found wandering"],[3810,3952,"Old Compton Street."],[3972,4060,"Interesting."],[4114,4214,"I believe I saw him on the"],[4214,4294,"guest list for the party."],[4302,4423,"I know. I put him there."],[4427,4677,"Always important to have a plan B."],[4748,5248,"Let go of me! Get off me. You idiots!"],[5361,5557,"Marcus! Tell them who I am!"],[5557,5733,"It's okay. Stand down."],[5741,5924,"Yeah, stand down, you big dummies."],[5933,6062,"You're lucky I don't get you fired."],[6316,6412,"Marcus, what the hell?"],[6458,6579,"I'm sorry, Gemma."],[6592,6838,"You're no longer on the list."],[6838,6934,"That's impossible."],[6959,7076,"Who took me off the list?"],[7117,7234,"Gemma?"],[7434,7559,"Hi, baby."],[7668,7818,"Did you miss me?"],[8469,8652,"So you're the coffee girl."],[8694,8936,"Huh. I'm Liam's girlfriend."],[8936,9123,"Ex-girlfriend."],[9153,9340,"Why do you say such hateful things?"],[9345,9453,"Because they're true."],[9545,9674,"Purple rain!"],[9732,9849,"Oh, hey."],[9912,10037,"Gemma."],[10091,10208,"I'm out."],[10341,10446,"Friend of yours?"],[10504,10654,"Ashok. Yeah."],[10842,10934,"Good friend."],[11417,11550,"You two should..."],[11645,11730,"Okay."],[11946,12146,"I'm so upset with you right now."]],"30":[[2,198,"Why? Because I'm defending"],[198,290,"my head of security?"],[290,456,"We should just fire him."],[463,607,"If we distanced ourselves from"],[607,761,"the parents of Liam's conquests,"],[761,990,"your party would be a wasteland."],[990,1241,"The boy likes his daughter. So what?"],[1245,1412,"He's hardly a boy,"],[1412,1570,"and what's got into you?"],[1574,1879,"For starters, my son died and"],[1879,2054,"we're throwing a garden party."],[2054,2225,"Our son. And have you forgotten"],[2225,2354,"what this event is about?"],[2363,2458,"It's for the families"],[2458,2567,"of soldiers and veterans."],[2571,2646,"Don't!"],[2738,2892,"Just don't say it's for Robert"],[2892,3042,"because we both know it isn't."],[3051,3101,"It is."],[3130,3213,"It's for you."],[3222,3389,"Oh, fine. It's for me."],[3389,3501,"I could do with a day"],[3501,3618,"simply enjoy myself."],[3626,3718,"Have some tea,"],[3718,3847,"meet up with some old friends."],[3852,3922,"Stop me from"],[3922,4077,"abolishing the monarchy."],[4319,4536,"I've been texting you."],[4640,4761,"I've had a few things going on."],[4836,4961,"So you get my pictures."],[5040,5094,"Yep."],[5119,5253,"I feel stupid about sending them now,"],[5253,5370,"considering you’re with her."],[5382,5466,"I’m not with her."],[5466,5591,"We’re just hanging out."],[5628,5708,"Good."],[5808,5962,"Because you're all mine."],[6008,6237,"And if I have to fight for you, I will."],[6329,6433,"Just to clarify,"],[6433,6500,"I don't mean in"],[6500,6588,"some romantic sense."],[6588,6875,"I actually will fight the bitch."],[6875,7117,"Gemma. You broke up with me."],[7117,7280,"Can we not do this?"],[7280,7380,"I mean, I said some things."],[7380,7463,"You said some things."],[7463,7522,"No, just..."],[7522,7643,"You said some things..."],[7672,7747,"ten months ago."],[7826,8018,"Then you disappeared."],[8018,8097,"Until now."],[8206,8310,"Meaning what?"],[8310,8435,"Meaning you disappeared."],[8502,8623,"Until now."],[8815,9057,"That's really sweet, Liam."],[9057,9244,"I chase you,"],[9244,9424,"I send you photos of my ass,"],[9424,9545,"amongst other things."],[9582,9883,"I try to apologize. And for what?"],[9903,10087,"So that you can imply that this is all"],[10087,10283,"some conspiracy to win you back."],[10283,10400,"Because you're suddenly next"],[10400,10521,"in line for the throne."],[10575,10654,"Gemma..."],[10654,10767,"That’s right. Isn’t it?"],[10767,10853,"That's what you meant."]],"31":[[873,1011,"It's not true."],[1190,1319,"I've made mistakes with you."],[1319,1461,"And a plan to fix them."],[1632,1761,"And you're going to let me."],[1961,2162,"Because it's like you said."],[2270,2533,"You're the next king of England."],[2541,2721,"And there aren't many girls out there"],[2721,2829,"who are going to understand"],[2829,3021,"what that means or know"],[3021,3125,"how to deal with it."],[3467,3596,"And you're going to need a girl like that."],[3767,3888,"So it may as well be"],[3888,3993,"the one that you ache"],[3993,4122,"for more than any other"],[4122,4260,"girl on the planet."],[4552,4852,"It's good to see you, baby."],[4931,5031,"I've missed you."],[5394,5528,"He likes you."],[5528,5619,"You're his wing man."],[5619,5732,"You have to say that."],[5765,5870,"Possibly true."],[5907,6007,"Okay, let me guess."],[6007,6307,"You’re studying dance."],[6366,6570,"No, no. Art history?"],[6633,6716,"Both."],[6750,6825,"Yeah."],[6825,7012,"You're also stubborn,"],[7012,7096,"competitive,"],[7096,7179,"a little awkward,"],[7179,7475,"and you like coffee."],[7567,7667,"Wait for it..."],[7667,7913,"Iced dirty chai with soy."],[8047,8180,"Okay, what the hell, dude?"],[8201,8314,"Well..."],[8314,8435,"Liam told me"],[8455,8556,"because he talks about you."],[8556,8760,"Because he likes you."],[8760,8910,"Oh, here he comes."],[8910,9002,"Don’t tell him I told you."],[9206,9381,"Little red Corvette."],[9431,9557,"Ashok likes to group me with"],[9557,9673,"songs by Prince."],[9903,10040,"I owe you an apology."],[10082,10178,"It's okay."],[10178,10253,"It's not okay."],[10253,10416,"And it's kind of a long story."],[10595,10799,"Ashok said you told him about me."],[10799,10941,"We’re so not friends anymore."],[10979,11208,"I, might have mentioned a thing"],[11208,11408,"or two about the awkward dork."],[11408,11567,"I'm inviting you to the garden party."],[11567,11705,"Sweet."],[11730,11800,"What time?"],[11876,11946,"Three o’clock for Ophelia."],[11946,12080,"Never o’clock for everyone else."],[12151,12326,"It's because I told her, isn't it?"],[12326,12443,"Okay, well I understand,"],[12443,12539,"but just so you know,"],[12539,12739,"I'm ashamed of myself."],[12772,12835,"Should be."],[12968,13006,"Come on."],[13006,13098,"We should go get you a hat."],[13302,13339,"Ashok,"],[13339,13440,"Thanks for hanging with Ophelia."],[13440,13531,"It's my pleasure."],[13531,13631,"I like this one."],[13631,13815,"She's dreadful at keeping secrets."],[13815,14015,"But other than that."],[14015,14178,"Well done, you."]],"32":[[32,162,"As you know, today is a"],[162,237,"once in a lifetime"],[237,408,"opportunity for many of our guests"],[408,537,"to meet a member of the Royal family."],[545,771,"So please, everyone, be regal"],[771,871,"and respectable."],[1113,1158,"Oh my God."],[1158,1279,"- I’m starving. - Did we miss it?"],[1342,1459,"Who invited them?"],[1480,1584,"I did."],[1584,1697,"I thought we could use them"],[1697,1809,"as human shields."],[1809,1984,"Just be aware of your surroundings."],[1984,2089,"Follow protocol when"],[2089,2168,"greeting the public"],[2168,2364,"and take no unnecessary risks."],[2906,2985,"I noticed that"],[2985,3156,"Gemma wasn't on the list,"],[3156,3286,"so I invited her."],[3315,3523,"Should make for splendid photo op."],[3590,3640,"See?"],[3686,3807,"There's nothing you can do"],[3807,3986,"that I can't fix."],[4028,4203,"Now then, it's imperative"],[4203,4337,"that you appear impressive today."],[4378,4679,"So please don't embarrass me."],[6856,6914,"How'd you do?"],[6964,7044,"How'd you do?"],[7044,7089,"You look wonderful."],[7089,7198,"Fabulous sari."],[10789,10902,"Fix this, Mother."],[12028,12328,"Son of a bitch."],[12708,12970,"I don't think this is very prudent, sir."],[13934,14096,"F-M-L."]],"33":[[1843,1935,"Can I have a word?"],[3273,3519,"Have you lost your goddamn mind?"],[3519,3648,"Pryce."],[3648,3944,"It is not now, nor in the history of time"],[3944,4099,"has it ever been okay for you"],[4099,4270,"to lose your shit with the future"],[4270,4432,"King of England."],[4603,4745,"Walk away."],[5066,5233,"He nearly gave it to you."],[5325,5513,"Which is fitting, considering"],[5513,5604,"how you gave it"],[5604,5717,"to his daughter."],[5996,6205,"You know, it's in everyone's"],[6205,6409,"best interest if you wake up"],[6409,6510,"one of these days."],[6597,6714,"I don't think you will."],[6747,6885,"But a man can dream."],[6914,7048,"What do you think's worse?"],[7098,7227,"Falling short at 21."],[7323,7494,"Falling short at 40."],[7494,7615,"Does it matter?"],[7615,7694,"Yes."],[7694,7894,"I still have time to change."],[7894,8036,"You have no time."],[8036,8186,"You have now."],[8186,8320,"You're one breath away from"],[8320,8445,"the greatest throne on earth,"],[8445,8620,"and you're squandering it all"],[8620,8820,"on schoolboy crushes and"],[8820,8991,"pints of beer in the pub."],[9075,9383,"And while nobody and I mean nobody"],[9383,9613,"appreciates excess and indulgence"],[9613,9704,"as much as I do,"],[9750,9934,"The fact that you fail to recognize"],[9934,10092,"the magnitude of what is slipping"],[10092,10192,"away from you"],[10192,10326,"is astounding to me,"],[10376,10559,"because it either means"],[10559,10689,"you're too stupid"],[10689,11022,"to understand it or you don't care."],[11022,11293,"And I have nothing but contempt"],[11293,11498,"and disdain for either one."],[11719,11836,"Men who would kill to"],[11836,12057,"stand where you're standing."],[12249,12453,"I would kill for it."]],"34":[[295,379,"How long do you think"],[379,496,"you can keep this up?"],[625,779,"How long can I or how long will I?"],[779,996,"Oh. Nice accent."],[996,1138,"You'll slip up,"],[1192,1363,"and when you do, you're going to jail."],[1363,1576,"So you'd better file a few things away"],[1576,1718,"in your wank bank, Jasper."],[2114,2260,"Who is that?"],[2347,2635,"Andy Sinclair, the Olympic swimmer."],[2635,2798,"Andy Sinclair won four gold medals"],[2798,2919,"in the last Olympic Games, including"],[2919,3073,"one of the greatest come from behind"],[3073,3219,"finishes in sports in history."],[3311,3469,"The guy inspired a Nation."],[3503,3732,"Does he inspire you?"],[3732,3861,"Well, yes, as a matter of fact,"],[3861,3970,"he does."],[4066,4304,"Swimmer, huh?"],[4908,5096,"I owe you an apology."],[5150,5275,"Umm..."],[5275,5367,"Ophelia."],[5388,5542,"Ophelia."],[5576,5647,"Why on earth"],[5647,5809,"did your parents call you that?"],[5809,5939,"Why’d they call you Gemma?"],[5984,6189,"I'm heiress to a diamond cartel."],[6243,6360,"Of course you are."],[6360,6481,"Don't be a bitch, okay?"],[6481,6589,"I'm trying to be nice."],[6614,6781,"It was a pleasure to see you again,"],[6781,6852,"as usual."],[7486,7615,"Au revoir."],[7974,8082,"How do you know how many times"],[8082,8162,"to fake kiss them?"],[8195,8341,"You can tell by their accent."],[8341,8545,"In France, it's either 2, 3 or 4."],[8633,8737,"Once in a while, 5"],[8762,8858,"Mostly just stick with 2 and"],[8858,8962,"you'll be fine."],[9021,9179,"Do you know how Liam and I met?"],[9259,9388,"We met onto Sir Richard's yacht"],[9388,9559,"in the British Virgin Islands."],[9605,9763,"At least we had the British"],[9763,9859,"and the islands part."],[9959,10051,"How did you two meet?"],[10143,10360,"I was drunk in a bar, called him an idiot."],[10497,10668,"I know how this is supposed to go."],[10802,10964,"I'm the hostile, pushy bitch"],[10964,11065,"with a fake smile"],[11065,11173,"and a secret agenda."],[11223,11386,"And you're the girl next door"],[11448,11661,"with pluck and charm"],[11661,11828,"and a quiet inner strength."],[11882,11961,"Advantage me."],[11995,12091,"You think?"],[12174,12303,"But we'll see about that?"],[12391,12499,"I can be you."],[12579,12691,"Can you be me?"],[13000,13125,"This morning didn't bother me,"],[13125,13246,"by the way."],[13246,13375,"No apology needed."],[13375,13534,"Oh, I wasn't sorry about that."],[13534,13675,"I'm apologizing in advance"],[13675,13834,"for winning Liam back."],[14130,14347,"By the way, the fork stays in your left, you"],[14347,14426,"lower your eyes when you"],[14426,14518,"meet the Chinese"],[14518,14706,"and the drinks at the bar are free."],[14847,14948,"And now you know."]],"35":[[220,359,"James Holloway."],[500,654,"Cyrus."],[654,800,"I was hoping to speak with you."],[800,858,"Oh?"],[913,1046,"To explain my absence"],[1046,1100,"this morning"],[1100,1209,"at the regional meeting."],[1209,1380,"Your responsibilities"],[1380,1522,"with Parliament are vast."],[1522,1655,"We understand."],[1697,1822,"Besides, it's a party."],[1822,2018,"Let's have a drink."],[2018,2226,"I'm afraid I've been officially sober"],[2226,2318,"now for eight hours."],[2335,2635,"Sounds like a party spent eight hours."],[3411,3599,"Guy Wells, British Farming Bureau."],[3599,3715,"Mr. Wells, how lovely"],[3715,3786,"to see you again."],[3786,3866,"Thank you, ma'am."],[3903,4074,"Poppy Rhodes, BBC."],[4074,4208,"Poppy. How are you?"],[4208,4358,"Very well, Your Majesty."],[4358,4429,"Thank you."],[4429,4587,"Captain Alistair Lacey,"],[4587,4775,"highly decorated war hero."],[4825,5054,"Captain Lacey, I'd like to"],[5054,5150,"personally thank you"],[5150,5317,"for your service and sacrifice."],[5350,5526,"It's my pleasure to serve the Queen."],[5901,6064,"Oh, Mr. Moody."],[6064,6176,"And how's the Chancellor"],[6176,6272,"of the Treasury?"],[6272,6502,"I'm hearing rumors of a referendum."],[6502,6714,"Talk of disbanding the monarchy."],[6714,6856,"Merely rumors, Winston."],[6856,6985,"You must hope so."],[6985,7135,"What will you do without"],[7135,7248,"the people's money?"],[7302,7528,"I expect we'll move to America."],[7528,7619,"What a shame the wedding"],[7619,7694,"will have to take place"],[7694,7761,"in the Hamptons."],[7911,8095,"Liam and Gemma."],[8095,8262,"What did our last wedding bring in?"],[8262,8453,"Two billion pounds?"],[8495,8712,"Hotels, shops, restaurants,"],[8758,8933,"Plus another three billion for the British"],[8933,9133,"designer who outfits the happy couple."],[9179,9279,"Never mind."],[9279,9442,"I'm sure Diane Von Furstenberg will"],[9442,9592,"be delighted to have the business."],[10176,10263,"You should ask yourself,"],[10279,10397,"“what will the people do without"],[10397,10493,"the monarchy's money?”"],[10818,10873,"You look like you could"],[10873,10956,"do with a drink."],[11231,11377,"I've never been on a yacht."],[11377,11511,"I switch hands with my fork,"],[11511,11648,"and I have a terrible habit"],[11648,11811,"of looking people in the eyes."],[11819,11949,"Chinese are not."],[11949,12024,"So, no."],[12024,12224,"Maybe I can't hang in your world."],[12224,12387,"But I have been to Kentucky."],[12387,12462,"Ever been."],[12491,12583,"God no."],[12825,12941,"They make bourbon there."],[13367,13534,"Welcome to my world."]],"36":[[304,441,"What do you call those muscles?"],[441,516,"Here."],[516,667,"I believe you mean the..."],[667,733,"obliques."],[733,804,"The obliques."],[863,938,"Definitely."],[938,1084,"And what do those taste like?"],[1497,1680,"Anyway, it was nice to meet you."],[1680,1780,"I'm extremely slutty."],[1780,1822,"Yes she is."],[1822,2018,"Like no holds barred."],[2018,2093,"Scurry."],[2314,2360,"Hi."],[2418,2502,"Your Highness."],[2535,2614,"It’s, it’s quite"],[2614,2727,"an honor to meet you."],[2827,2940,"That, that comeback"],[2940,3090,"in that swimming race..."],[3173,3273,"inspired me."],[3273,3444,"It's very kind of you to say."],[3444,3745,"And you must be in magnificent shape."],[3786,3861,"Excuse me, your Highness"],[3861,3962,"may I have a word, please?"],[4066,4270,"This is my my bodyguard, Jasper."],[4312,4399,"He's not supposed to speak"],[4399,4520,"until he's spoken to,"],[4520,4775,"but he's a big fan of yours, so I think"],[4775,4933,"he's a little bit out of his depth."],[4937,5063,"It's good to meet you, Jasper."],[5125,5238,"Where are you from?"],[5238,5367,"Yes, Jasper."],[5367,5463,"Where are you from?"],[5509,5584,"It's okay to answer."],[5584,5738,"I give you permission."],[5826,5943,"Well, go ahead."],[6018,6143,"Speak."],[6318,6435,"Shoreditch, actually."],[6502,6614,"Shoreditch."],[6685,6760,"Your Highness."],[6885,6935,"Yes."],[7090,7282,"Excuse me."],[7653,7782,"What do you think you're doing?"],[7911,8011,"Right now, I'm"],[8011,8245,"I'm flirting with your hero."],[8245,8299,"And, umm,"],[8299,8516,"and pretty soon, I'm going to de-hero"],[8516,8595,"your hero."],[8741,8812,"And there's not a thing"],[8812,8916,"you can do about it."],[8916,9008,"Because out here,"],[9008,9225,"you're simply Jasper, my"],[9225,9350,"speak-upon-spoken-to"],[9404,9542,"British bodyguard."],[9709,9776,"And by the way,"],[9776,9922,"your accent is slipping."],[10084,10230,"My apologies."],[10343,10501,"Prudence."],[10635,10777,"Your Majesty."],[10777,10927,"May I be of service?"],[11023,11165,"What do you think of all this?"],[11298,11398,"The spectacle."],[11511,11607,"The monarchy."],[11744,11828,"I would appreciate"],[11828,11940,"your honest opinion."],[12103,12249,"I'm happy to be employed"],[12249,12399,"in Your Majesty's home."],[12441,12637,"But if I'm to be honest,"],[12637,12770,"I find some members"],[12770,12954,"of your household to be..."],[13125,13317,"Reprehensible."],[13367,13433,"So do I."],[13488,13763,"I find this whole event intolerable."],[14038,14213,"So, what do you do next?"],[14284,14497,"I prepare the fruit tartlets."],[14497,14668,"Well, that sounds like more fun than"],[14668,14881,"making small talk with heads of State."],[15039,15156,"May I join you?"]],"37":[[52,215,"Say yes, Prudence."],[340,461,"I am the king of England."],[523,715,"Of course, Your Majesty."],[1470,1590,"Had enough?"],[1837,2112,"You know, it's funny, my world."],[2112,2420,"Lunches, galas and events."],[2454,2625,"Bloody Marys in the morning."],[2630,2846,"Mimosas for brunch."],[2892,3151,"Expensive wines by the barrel"],[3151,3334,"and bottle service in the clubs."],[3993,4189,"A girl builds up her tolerance."],[5345,5545,"Welcome to my world, Kentucky."],[8819,8936,"Excuse me!"],[9653,9774,"Is that Ophelia?"],[9878,9999,"I believe it is, sir."],[10075,10216,"She's pretty great, isn't she, Marcus?"],[10291,10425,"She is indeed, sir."],[10875,11059,"Did she just pass out?"],[11155,11272,"She did indeed, sir."]],"38":[[831,941,"How you doing, Rihanna?"],[1328,1526,"I showed her."],[1592,1772,"Right. Here we go..."],[2100,2256,"Hey. We're here."],[2276,2343,"Ophelia."],[2355,2543,"I can do it. I can do it."],[2745,2780,"Hey, umm..."],[2780,2865,"Let me, let me..."],[2866,2981,"No, I said I can do it."],[2981,3057,"Okay."],[3382,3513,"No, I can't do it."],[3522,3596,"All right."],[4062,4223,"Go ahead. Hats."],[4478,4609,"Easy, easy."],[4616,4700,"All right."],[4700,4804,"Wait, wait, wait. Put me down."],[4804,4833,"Put me down."],[4833,4903,"Okay. Okay."],[4903,5090,"The room spinning. It’s not good..."],[5102,5253,"It's not good at all."],[5253,5341,"Okay, easy."],[5347,5471,"I got you. I got you."],[5533,5665,"All right."],[6238,6429,"You dated her."],[6461,6528,"Uh, yep."],[6622,6818,"Why? I mean..."],[6880,7007,"How could you do that?"],[7082,7222,"She was my first love."],[7991,8129,"Wow."],[8587,8678,"It's okay..."],[8737,8850,"You got this."]],"39":[[56,311,"The King of Hearts called for the tarts."],[770,891,"Did you know the King of Hearts is"],[891,949,"the only king"],[949,1053,"without a moustache"],[1053,1166,"on playing cards?"],[1199,1433,"Clubs, spades, diamonds."],[1462,1612,"All moustaches."],[1704,1912,"He's also called the suicide King"],[1912,2054,"because he appears to be"],[2054,2175,"stabbing himself,"],[2217,2279,"although it's"],[2279,2350,"debatable whether or not"],[2350,2559,"it's his hand doing the stabbing."],[2747,2922,"Do you have children, Prudence?"],[2997,3101,"Not yet."],[3193,3339,"I would like to, one day."],[3426,3610,"Children are wondrous."],[3618,3768,"They change everything."],[4006,4119,"What is your life like"],[4119,4265,"outside of these walls?"],[4265,4344,"Do you have a good life?"],[4407,4519,"I read."],[4578,4690,"Mostly the classics."],[4719,4878,"I just finished The Great Gatsby."],[5074,5203,"\"The loneliest moment in"],[5203,5320,"someone's life"],[5428,5549,"is when they are watching their"],[5549,5691,"whole world fall apart,"],[5691,5950,"and all they can do is stare blankly.\""],[6834,6992,"How you doing, Rock Star?"],[7047,7234,"Throwing up egg salad with the future"],[7234,7401,"King of England in the next room."],[7439,7547,"Why all the mayonnaise?"],[7618,7689,"Why?"],[7893,8018,"It's absurd, isn't it?"],[8077,8202,"The mayonnaise?"],[8323,8494,"\"The future king of England.\""],[8548,8652,"I remember the day I realized"],[8652,8765,"Robert was gonna be the next king"],[8765,8873,"and I never would be."],[9028,9136,"I was just a kid."],[9220,9345,"I remember feeling relieved."],[9553,9649,"I think if you're meant to be king,"],[9649,9770,"you wouldn't feel that way."],[9770,9950,"Well, as long as we're sharing,"],[10171,10371,"I have a confession to make."],[10488,10571,"You were just supposed to be"],[10571,10671,"my story."],[10721,10859,"When I slept with you."],[10909,11159,"\"I got drunk and slept with a prince.\""],[11322,11464,"I know that sounds terrible"],[11597,11793,"but I don't really have a story,"],[11868,11922,"ya know?"],[12064,12302,"Well, now you have two."],[12369,12561,"One involves vomiting."]],"40":[[96,233,"I was sad you invited Gemma."],[329,496,"She speaks French."],[496,680,"She's named after the best jewel."],[778,959,"She drinks bourbon way better than me."],[1059,1255,"My mom invited her."],[1309,1389,"Really?"],[1434,1505,"I wouldn't do that."],[1827,1927,"Why not?"],[2014,2152,"Because I invited you."],[2473,2631,"I just wanted a story."],[2736,2794,"You weren't supposed"],[2794,2882,"to be nice."],[3420,3637,"I can't believe we're in the Palace."],[3637,3920,"This place is so amazing."],[3929,4037,"You know what's even"],[4037,4154,"more amazing?"],[4212,4350,"My bedroom."],[4542,4684,"Is that appropriate?"],[4813,4950,"Is this appropriate?"],[5584,5693,"I'm going in."],[5772,5943,"You'll want to join me."],[5943,6143,"I, too, have inspired a nation."],[6852,6952,"People always say that"],[6952,7103,"comeback inspired them."],[7199,7340,"But you know what it means to me?"],[7482,7624,"It means I get to add a princess"],[7624,7874,"to a long list of desperate sluts."],[8033,8099,"Andy."],[8216,8308,"I'm sorry, I'll probably"],[8308,8400,"lose my job for this but"],[8400,8512,"could I get a photo?"],[8708,8909,"Anything for the little people."],[11023,11219,"What did you do? Did you kill him?"],[11328,11411,"Maybe."],[11428,11586,"You can't do that!"],[12229,12320,"Is he dead?"],[12450,12533,"Maybe."],[13175,13230,"I always wondered how"],[13230,13326,"I’d lose my virginity."],[13338,13451,"Tonight's the night, Fridgy."],[13638,13889,"You can't do this."]],"41":[[108,254,"I know I can't fix you a drink,"],[254,337,"considering drink, your nine"],[337,500,"hours of sobriety, but is there"],[500,612,"anything else I can get you?"],[616,704,"No. Please. You've been"],[704,829,"uncommonly gracious today."],[829,1046,"Of course. But I feel like there"],[1046,1209,"must be something I can do for you."],[1217,1359,"Cyrus, there's nothing I need."],[1430,1513,"That's not the word on"],[1513,1609,"Old Compton Street."],[1772,1880,"I can explain."],[1943,2101,"We all have our desires, James."],[2531,2689,"And quite frankly..."],[2990,3119,"You've become much more alluring"],[3119,3328,"to me since yours came to light."],[3711,3828,"Party's nearly finished."],[3891,4041,"I should probably take off."],[4374,4470,"Word of advice,"],[4562,4708,"maybe stick to coffee for a while."],[4879,5000,"Yeah. Thanks."],[5004,5079,"Besides, If we keep having"],[5079,5175,"coffee together,"],[5175,5359,"it might eventually turn into a real date."],[5646,5722,"About that."],[5826,6043,"The thing is, I'm not posh,"],[6043,6205,"I don't speak French,"],[6205,6368,"I've never owned a designer"],[6368,6468,"dress in my life."],[6489,6618,"None of which matters."],[6685,6789,"I think it does."],[6952,7052,"I'm sorry."],[7494,7586,"I guess I should go."],[8508,8595,"Hey."],[8804,8979,"For what it's worth, I think"],[8979,9142,"you'll be an amazing King."],[9346,9421,"Thank you."],[9550,9721,"No one's ever said that to me before."]],"42":[[40,177,"Successful day, Mr. Pryce?"],[207,461,"No shots fired from the grassy knoll?"],[469,603,"Without incident."],[636,745,"Without incident?"],[782,941,"Liam missed a very important meeting"],[941,1083,"this morning because of Ophelia."],[1116,1212,"He could have repaired things"],[1212,1279,"this afternoon"],[1279,1441,"but once again your daughter"],[1441,1579,"ferreted him away"],[1596,1675,"by making herself"],[1675,1817,"an alcoholic spectacle."],[1854,1917,"And for what?"],[1971,2033,"Love?"],[2092,2280,"He's the future King of England."],[2288,2584,"Love has nothing to do with it. Fix it."],[2592,2788,"And what of your son's heart?"],[3018,3122,"Men have reached great"],[3122,3306,"heights with wounded hearts."],[3439,3573,"Shall I check Your Majesty's room?"],[3631,3744,"Because of the threats?"],[3823,3998,"It's my bedroom, Mr. Pryce."],[3998,4069,"You can no longer be of"],[4069,4177,"any service to me."],[4248,4390,"But don't take it personally."],[4444,4644,"Sadly, not many can."],[7439,7577,"What are you doing in here?"],[7710,7802,"You expect me to get that"],[7802,7969,"close to you and just walk away?"],[8844,9124,"I want to personally thank you for your"],[9124,9295,"service and sacrifice,"],[9295,9408,"Captain Lacey."],[9458,9654,"It's my pleasure to serve the queen."]],"43":[[329,359,"Go."],[1571,1634,"Helly."],[1897,2001,"I love you."],[2126,2268,"I love you, too."],[3427,3540,"I'm sure you'll agree that"],[3540,3757,"discretion is in our best interests."],[3953,4145,"Your secrets are safe with me."],[4232,4408,"Of course in exchange, Helena"],[4408,4595,"is going to need a little favor."],[4654,4787,"From one Queen to another."],[4850,4975,"If I refuse?"],[4975,5071,"You won't."],[5834,6088,"Say hi to the wife and kids for me."],[8124,8207,"We're not going to have another"],[8207,8337,"day like we had today."],[8574,8754,"Cause if we do, I'm releasing the video."],[9117,9250,"No, you won't."],[9350,9517,"Because if you do,"],[9659,9984,"all this goes away."],[10368,10580,"Don't make false threats, Jasper."],[10681,10835,"It makes you less interesting."],[11577,11777,"No blackmail sex tonight?"]],"44":[[1724,1874,"Day drinking remedy."],[2662,2758,"Urgh."],[3012,3179,"I need your help."],[5715,5836,"We lost you at the party."],[5915,6020,"I was with Ophelia."],[6207,6357,"Sorry about the crowdsurfing."],[6416,6562,"It looked fun."],[6695,6933,"Besides, there are some monarchs on"],[6933,7012,"these walls who have"],[7012,7167,"done much worse."],[7388,7504,"And one in this room who has"],[7504,7600,"done much better."],[7646,7721,"Not always."],[7896,7992,"Dad, I've been thinking about the"],[7992,8213,"monarchy, my place in it."],[8314,8414,"All that I ask is that you give me a"],[8414,8589,"little time before you go to Parliament."],[8610,8714,"Time to find a different side of me."],[8714,8777,"Son..."],[8789,8881,"You told me to chose my"],[8881,9023,"own path and not the throne."],[9085,9169,"But I have a purpose now,"],[9169,9252,"I never had before."],[9335,9419,"But anyway, why should I"],[9419,9515,"have to choose?"],[9552,9702,"Isn't it possible that I can have both?"],[9765,9848,"Love and the Crown?"],[9932,10082,"It has to be possible, Dad."],[10103,10190,"Of course it is."],[10190,10345,"I know I've made mistakes."],[10436,10520,"But I'd give it all up"],[10520,10612,"to have Robert back."],[11137,11250,"I've been told that I might make"],[11250,11367,"a great king, one day."],[11579,11717,"Just give me a chance."],[12359,12451,"Okay."]],"45":[[4792,4892,"I am reconsidering"],[4892,5021,"disbanding the monarchy..."],[5088,5196,"giving Liam some"],[5196,5321,"time to prove himself."],[5718,5822,"I'm reconsidering"],[5822,5918,"some things as well,"],[5980,6106,"Your Majesty."],[9067,9209,"That is so your move."],[11240,11378,"If you're going to be completely"],[11378,11532,"preoccupied by another woman,"],[11532,11653,"you could at least fake it"],[11703,11786,"until I'm gone."],[11911,12003,"It's complicated."],[12103,12216,"It always is."]],"46":[[160,331,"She have anything for you yet?"],[385,431,"Who?"],[518,585,"Ophelia."],[752,873,"You’re texting her to try and find out"],[873,1073,"something to use against me."],[1085,1286,"I'm not texting Ophelia."],[1286,1432,"Ophelia has access to Ted"],[1432,1582,"who has access to me."],[1661,1799,"That would be my play."],[2187,2366,"I'm from Nevada."],[2416,2579,"I grew up outside Las Vegas."],[2579,2758,"My parents were grifters and thieves"],[2758,2850,"whose hearts were broken"],[2850,2962,"when their only son decided"],[2962,3129,"to work security in the casinos."],[3188,3296,"Eventually, he became"],[3296,3388,"the best there was."],[3471,3555,"They disowned him,"],[3555,3684,"not that it mattered."],[3721,3888,"And he wound up in the bed"],[3888,4018,"of a princess."],[4097,4305,"The Princess."],[4351,4551,"And not that I believe you."],[4585,4706,"Why'd you leave?"],[4735,4802,"You know, if you had it"],[4802,4973,"so good in Las Vegas?"],[5010,5198,"Because Las Vegas is a goddamn"],[5198,5344,"impossible way of life."],[5377,5507,"So is blackmail."],[5615,5840,"You have a panic button right there."],[5995,6195,"All you have to do is press it."],[6416,6616,"You might have the upper hand"],[6633,6808,"right now, Jasper,"],[6808,6941,"from wherever."],[7033,7183,"What you don't have is permission"],[7183,7396,"to be here in the mornings."],[7396,7809,"Bringing that smug, arrogant, “I win”"],[7834,7967,"look on your face."],[8113,8288,"Now, get off!"],[8288,8384,"And get out!"],[8447,8497,"Now!"],[8939,9139,"Last night was fun."],[9256,9456,"Let me know what Ophelia finds out."],[11704,11905,"Ophelia! Ophelia!"],[12105,12326,"Ophelia! Ophelia!"],[12772,12972,"Ophelia! Ophelia!"],[13022,13206,"Ophelia! Ophelia!"],[13206,13335,"Let go of me!"]],"47":[[0,155,"Oh, Ophelia my... I-I-It’s me!"],[192,263,"Nick."],[263,346,"Who?"],[346,547,"Nick Roane from..."],[630,826,"I write the music you rehearse to."],[826,1026,"Oh, sorry."],[1047,1214,"Really made an impression."],[1322,1460,"You better go."],[1460,1652,"Need a ride?"],[1652,1831,"Yeah, I guess I do."],[1831,1994,"I’m not a stalker, Ophelia."],[2086,2248,"I have to imagine all stalkers say that"],[2307,2415,"before they stalk."],[2440,2524,"Likely true."],[2611,2761,"Who are you, anyway?"],[2795,2907,"What?"],[2978,3074,"You just said..."],[3074,3162,"To them,"],[3162,3303,"the paps."],[3303,3395,"Doesn't really matter."],[3445,3579,"Pretty much just live in my studio"],[3579,3700,"and avoid social media."],[3804,3908,"That's odd."],[4075,4159,"You're being chased"],[4159,4338,"by desperate, overweight men"],[4338,4438,"with digital cameras,"],[4488,4642,"and I'm the odd one?"],[4788,4893,"Hop on."],[6119,6211,"Fantastic."],[6211,6344,"No, that's great news."],[6344,6544,"Her Majesty will be pleased."],[6569,6648,"Goodbye."],[6790,6907,"Good news."],[6907,7049,"Tom Ford just personally delivered"],[7049,7145,"a few new peices."],[7224,7299,"What’s Eleanor wearing?"],[7328,7520,"Whatever she woke up in I assume,"],[7520,7633,"minus the knickers."],[7633,7875,"My predecessors saved Prussia,"],[7875,7966,"and I'm posing"],[7966,8092,"for London Fashion Week."],[8133,8275,"You're promoting British designers."],[8275,8442,"Then why do I have to wear this?"],[8442,8584,"Someone needs to look royal."],[8584,8734,"Ridiculous."],[8734,8801,"I don't even get to"],[8801,8926,"wear Alexander McQueen."],[9222,9385,"Oh, Liam."],[9410,9497,"You look tired, darling."],[9497,9576,"Come here."],[9973,10160,"I smell supermodel."],[10160,10260,"Poor Gemma."],[10644,10748,"Good god."],[10748,10903,"You can't wear that for the photo shoot."],[10903,11090,"Oh, this? I haven’t changed yet."],[11090,11224,"Mine’s supposed to be ironic."],[11462,11662,"C’mon, frosty."],[11954,12046,"Liam,"],[12046,12150,"I know this is normally the week"],[12150,12208,"you feed,"],[12208,12408,"but your schedule is exhaustive."],[12408,12609,"Welcome to the rare air my son."],[12634,12750,"And if it’s any consolation,"],[12750,12930,"your father's in a foul mood."],[12930,13105,"Well, I think you and Liberace"],[13105,13188,"might have something to"],[13188,13259,"do with that."],[13259,13405,"Oh my peacock."],[13409,13470,"Any news?"]],"48":[[12,117,"The seeds you planted at the"],[117,275,"garden party flowered nicely."],[333,421,"Chancellor Moody has"],[421,521,"given an interview"],[521,738,"extolling the virtues and importance"],[738,805,"of the monarchy,"],[805,905,"now more than ever."],[963,1059,"What in God's name"],[1059,1163,"did you promise him?"],[1176,1259,"Liam’s wedding"],[1297,1510,"and 9 billion British Pounds."],[1581,1626,"Front cover?"],[1626,1735,"No, we’re trying."],[1735,1772,"You know,"],[1772,1889,"they always reserve the cover"],[1889,2060,"for some slut in lingerie."],[2094,2252,"I want the front page."],[2252,2335,"Let me know when it runs."],[3524,3624,"This is perfect."],[3624,3724,"Thank you."],[3724,3841,"You live in a cheese shop?"],[4100,4242,"No, I just."],[4242,4442,"You still think I'm a stalker?"],[4454,4646,"No, I umm..."],[4646,4846,"It's fine."],[4921,5122,"It was good to finally talk to you."],[5138,5338,"I've wanted to."],[5543,5635,"Thank you."],[5635,5751,"I appreciate it."],[5751,5910,"It's what I do."],[5910,6110,"Well, actually, it's not that."],[6173,6348,"I'm glad I did."],[6348,6544,"I'll see you."],[7812,7983,"Classic or avant garde?"],[7983,8183,"Either way, you look stunning in purple."],[8200,8287,"It's regal."],[8287,8408,"It's elegant."],[8408,8490,"It's taken."],[8583,8779,"Absolutely not."],[8779,9009,"You know I'm wearing purple."],[9009,9067,"You purpos–"],[9067,9130,"Bagsy."],[9176,9255,"You can’t call bagsy."],[9267,9401,"I can, and I did."],[9401,9547,"I call bagsy on purple."],[9564,9676,"So purple is mine."],[9747,9830,"Bagsy."],[9830,9901,"Lucius?"],[9910,10114,"What? Regrettably,"],[10114,10298,"there is no higher authority"],[10298,10381,"than bagsy,"],[10381,10456,"Your Majesty."],[10556,10756,"Oh, for God's sake."],[10936,11078,"Oh, the cover?"],[11078,11198,"Page two."],[11198,11303,"Well, who got the cover?"],[11303,11436,"Another slut in ingerie?"],[11436,11624,"Your words, not mine."],[11661,11707,"Oh!"],[12204,12250,"And that..."],[12250,12391,"Her Majesty, the Queen recently"],[12391,12458,"wastes the people’s"],[12458,12529,"hard earned money,"],[12529,12754,"over 50,000 pounds, on a small"],[12754,12950,"batch of overpriced lingerie."],[12996,13096,"How did they get this?"],[13096,13205,"This has to be an inside job."],[13205,13317,"It certainly was."],[13317,13447,"It seems their informant"],[13447,13609,"is standing in this very room"],[13668,13868,"wearing purple."],[14193,14247,"Well?"]],"49":[[51,126,"That's for messing"],[126,226,"with my social media."],[355,472,"At least they photoshopped"],[472,609,"your face on a younger woman's"],[609,710,"body, Mother."],[856,918,"Walk away."],[960,1110,"Everyone but you, go."],[2132,2332,"Do you think this hurts me?"],[2357,2516,"It seems like it somewhat"],[2516,2703,"upsets you, yes."],[2732,2837,"It doesn't."],[2874,2974,"It hurts you"],[3037,3237,"because when the people read this"],[3237,3337,"and when they vote to"],[3337,3479,"disband the monarchy,"],[3533,3629,"you're gonna realize"],[3629,3738,"that you need this world"],[3738,3938,"more than any of us."],[4180,4313,"Remind me what your talents are"],[4313,4413,"other than ingesting"],[4413,4518,"other people's drugs"],[4518,4601,"and being young and"],[4655,4755,"somewhat attractive."],[4810,4864,"For now."],[5277,5477,"You do nothing."],[5514,5715,"You contribute nothing."],[5781,5982,"When all this goes away,"],[5982,6182,"you're gonna be..."],[6219,6294,"nothing."],[6495,6695,"Yes, and you'll be the same,"],[6720,6920,"only older."],[7099,7320,"No, I'll be fine."],[7445,7646,"We both know you won't be."],[8326,8488,"Dad, I’m home."]],"50":[[99,258,"What’s bagsy?"],[401,513,"Well, you should know"],[513,643,"Jasper from Shoreditch."],[680,839,"I mean, Nevada."],[926,1131,"Bagsy is like ‘dibs’ in America."],[1131,1331,"So I call Bagsy on the color purple."],[1331,1544,"So purple is mine no matter what."],[1606,1706,"Oh the purple, it's nice."],[1706,1798,"But for what it's worth,"],[1798,1915,"you look sexier in black."],[1977,2061,"Yes, well,"],[2061,2186,"that might be worth something"],[2186,2240,"if it weren't"],[2240,2365,"coming from you, Jasper."],[2365,2565,"But as it is, it's worth nothing."],[2603,2699,"Off you go."],[2978,3120,"So, Princess,"],[3120,3291,"still licking your wounds"],[3291,3416,"after our little tiff?"],[3450,3650,"Far too busy to lick my wounds, Mother."],[3650,3808,"I have a fashion show to plan."],[3833,3946,"You have a what?"],[3946,4067,"A fashion show."],[4067,4155,"My fashion show,"],[4221,4346,"which just so happens"],[4346,4438,"to be on the"],[4438,4601,"same night as your fashion show."],[4651,4814,"Don’t be so ridiculous."],[4814,4964,"You know my event is the pinnacle"],[4964,5043,"of Fashion Week."],[5076,5181,"You'll be setting yourself up"],[5181,5318,"for illicit public scrutiny,"],[5339,5518,"not to mention global ridicule"],[5518,5564,"from the press"],[5564,5777,"when your show is less than mine."],[5906,6015,"Unless, of course,"],[6015,6119,"it's more than yours."],[6119,6240,"Which it will be."],[6298,6436,"You want to call me nothing."],[6436,6686,"You say I have no talent."],[6832,6991,"Okay, well,I guess now we'll see."],[7074,7191,"Game on, Queen."],[7404,7483,"Look,"],[7529,7666,"it's my location scout"],[7666,7746,"for my fashion show."],[7804,7950,"I'll have to take this."],[8033,8125,"Speak."],[8204,8350,"I love it."],[8392,8425,"Yep."],[8425,8626,"Best location ever."],[8626,8747,"Our show is gonna be"],[8747,8851,"the talk of fashion week."],[9005,9039,"Excuse me."]],"51":[[84,184,"You're late."],[226,321,"Sorry."],[321,434,"You said you wanted to dedicate"],[434,547,"yourself to the monarchy,"],[547,626,"and you show up"],[643,776,"drunk and tardy."],[809,930,"I'm not drunk."],[930,1131,"I'm hungover."],[1143,1222,"and I'm five minutes late"],[1222,1306,"because mom insisted"],[1306,1402,"I try on every last"],[1402,1539,"Matthew Owens suit in England"],[1539,1602,"for the photo shoot."],[1719,1848,"You're wearing Matthew Owens?"],[1848,1902,"Yes."],[1931,2040,"What's Cyrus wearing?"],[2052,2115,"Alexander McQueen,"],[2115,2157,"I suppose."],[2161,2269,"Son of a bitch."],[2399,2586,"They get under my skin,"],[2586,2753,