n's talking all about"],[576,718,"this abolishment nonsense."],[1348,1431,"Who knew?"],[1556,1690,"Four minutes earlier"],[1690,1857,"and she'd have been the next heir."],[1857,2065,"At least someone enjoyed their day."],[2412,2574,"Why can't I ever remember how"],[2574,2749,"awful coming down off ex is"],[2749,2900,"before taking it?"],[3137,3300,"Effing brutal."],[3550,3792,"And those poor old people."],[3792,3930,"They’re just going to die soon,"],[3930,4001,"you know?"],[4167,4309,"Those poor animals."],[4376,4534,"And they’re going to die too."],[4781,4989,"It’s a dreadful world we live in."],[5377,5540,"Which, of course,"],[5540,5794,"always leads me back to you, Jasper."],[5907,6044,"Is this where you"],[6103,6290,"take advantage of me again?"],[6766,6866,"Is that what you want?"],[7179,7316,"Of course not."],[7446,7700,"Who would want any of this?"],[10140,10253,"Bloody hell."],[10253,10349,"Marcus, be a dear and"],[10349,10449,"fetch my earrings."],[10449,10578,"I left them on the vanity."],[10578,10661,"I know you didn't just"],[10661,10807,"mistake me for a footman."],[10953,11116,"Well, there's no need for attitude."],[11116,11183,"No attitude."],[11283,11383,"Just fact."],[11437,11533,"Not a footman."],[11604,11838,"Okay. Like facts do you?"],[11838,11913,"Here’s one."],[11942,12134,"I'll be around for a while now."],[12175,12313,"You don't want to help a friend out?"],[12313,12396,"Fine."],[12426,12567,"But it's best for everyone that you"],[12567,12626,"and I have a"],[12626,12747,"meaningful relationship."],[12780,12847,"Don't you remember"],[12847,12993,"giving me this speech last year?"],[13068,13168,"Before you broke his heart"],[13168,13347,"by running off to Madagascar after..."],[13393,13506,"Who was it that time?"],[13589,13735,"Ryan Reynolds."],[13819,13948,"Leaving Liam here to pick up the"],[13948,14036,"pieces of himself"],[14036,14136,"that you trampled on."]],"72":[[27,177,"And now you pop back up"],[177,390,"at a suspiciously coincidental time"],[406,561,"and expect him to hand those pieces"],[561,632,"right back to you like"],[632,711,"nothing ever happened."],[844,990,"Just because you're a good lay."],[1166,1303,"That's the most I've ever heard you"],[1303,1395,"speak, Marcus."],[1395,1578,"And in complete sentences."],[1578,1679,"Well, I have a few more"],[1679,1783,"complete sentences for you,"],[1895,1929,"but I'm"],[1929,2100,"not sure you could recover from them."],[2304,2408,"I've always admired"],[2408,2709,"your straight faced sass, Marcus,"],[2721,2826,"but I expect the charm"],[2826,2951,"will wear off soon."],[3618,3781,"Not a good lay, by the way."],[3847,4039,"Great lay."],[4644,4786,"How do you do?"],[4786,4999,"Wonderful to meet you. How do you do?"],[5449,5578,"So, this is what big"],[5578,5737,"John Middleton grew up?"],[5737,5808,"Yeah."],[6304,6521,"How do you do, wonderful people?"],[6684,6821,"Got to say, I feel sorry for you."],[6888,6976,"Yeah."],[6976,7101,"Supporting Liverpool must be a"],[7101,7205,"real bitch."],[7267,7384,"Each season, a bigger"],[7384,7514,"disappointment than the last."],[7514,7664,"And who is it you support?"],[7664,7739,"Let me guess."],[7739,7901,"Those Chelsea toss pots."],[7901,7960,"I bleed blue."],[7960,8097,"Oh, piss off."],[8097,8156,"Now hold on."],[8156,8231,"If we’re going to keep arguing"],[8231,8335,"about football,"],[8335,8477,"I think we should do it in proper fashion."],[8677,8798,"With pints of beers in our hand."],[8840,8915,"You've got a pub?"],[8965,9048,"Have we got a pub?"],[9048,9207,"C’mon. C’mon, lads."],[9582,9853,"How do you do?"],[9853,9903,"Your Majesty."],[9903,9995,"And how do you do?"],[9995,10120,"Oh, another little one."],[10120,10183,"How do you do?"],[10295,10412,"Do you live in a palace"],[10412,10575,"like in all the stories?"],[10575,10663,"I do."],[10746,10963,"My mummy reads me all the stories"],[10963,11113,"about all the princesses"],[11113,11171,"and queens"],[11171,11309,"every single night."],[11413,11530,"Where is your mummy, darling?"],[11530,11634,"She couldn't come."],[11634,11772,"Our cows got sick."],[11801,11851,"Oh."],[12093,12335,"Well, she can't miss her opportunity"],[12335,12393,"to meet the Queen"],[12393,12481,"now, can she?"],[12539,12623,"Come on darling."]],"73":[[105,272,"Maybe I try it sober today."],[368,514,"Yeah. I mean, yesterday was fun,"],[514,760,"sure, but perhaps I owe it to these"],[760,927,"poor plebs to put the Crown's"],[927,1019,"best foot forward."],[1110,1261,"You know, for dad, at least."],[1261,1373,"How admirable."],[1548,1849,"So, what is first stop on the tour today?"],[1853,2153,"Saint Luke's children's hospital."],[2487,2630,"I need a drink."],[3029,3246,"Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!"],[3246,3463,"Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!"],[3813,3951,"Another round please."],[4097,4255,"You seem charming."],[4255,4460,"Like you’re good fun."],[4460,4572,"Thank you."],[4572,4660,"Those aren't the qualities"],[4660,4789,"I want from my king."],[4852,5002,"Seems that's just me, though."],[5069,5198,"What is it you want from you king?"],[5348,5473,"Someone who recognizes"],[5473,5615,"when they have the power to make"],[5615,5765,"the world a better place."],[5778,6036,"Someone who changes lives"],[6036,6320,"and inspires all of us to do the same."],[6320,6512,"Do that, and then I’ll say"],[6512,6670,"you've done something."],[6670,6875,"Then I'd call you my king."],[6975,7196,"Liam! Liam!"],[7196,7371,"Aye, afar cross flew."],[7371,7579,"You’re half crazy"],[7579,7730,"after a brew or two."],[7730,7955,"There are 52 cars in the garage."],[8005,8088,"You know,"],[8088,8359,"I grew up on a farm very much like this."],[8359,8656,"Then I grew up to be Queen."],[8751,8931,"Your Majesty, please forgive my"],[8931,9052,"absence at the greeting."],[9056,9131,"But the cows..."],[9131,9202,"The cows."],[9202,9356,"Your daughter told me."],[9356,9444,"I'm sorry to hear that"],[9444,9527,"they've become ill."],[9527,9636,"Yeah. It's happening to all the"],[9636,9740,"village livestock."],[9740,9869,"It's because of the new labeling"],[9869,10032,"process the distillery uses."],[10032,10207,"It's poisoning the groundwater."],[10345,10545,"150 years it's been there."],[10545,10733,"And the owner passes and his son"],[10733,10883,"starts cutting costs on the labeling"],[10937,11054,"and dumping all the chemicals"],[11054,11141,"in our stream."],[11221,11379,"And now we all have to suffer."],[11830,11996,"Tell the press to return to the plane."],[12584,12668,"I understand"],[12668,12835,"she's the Queen of England,"],[12835,13014,"but the woman is a complete cow."],[13047,13181,"And between you and me,"],[13181,13352,"I think she's had little work done."],[13473,13585,"Do you know what I mean?"],[13840,14028,"Nope. Never mind."],[14111,14357,"Now, who else here hates their mother?"],[14716,14958,"This is the privileged paella"],[14958,15225,"Saturday at Casa Francesca."],[15225,15421,"Lucky for you, you know someone."],[15421,15713,"Oh, they’re here averyone. Let's eat."]],"74":[[667,847,"Hi. Nice to meet you."],[851,930,"Enjoy."],[1009,1114,"Want to give me a plate?"],[2327,2490,"Cheers, everyone."],[2490,2611,"Cheers."],[2694,2840,"Cheers."],[5226,5451,"Saddle maker, yeah?"],[5451,5568,"It's okay."],[5568,5693,"Stay seated. It's all right."],[5839,6073,"May I? I play a bit of polo."],[6452,6561,"You're good."],[6561,6753,"Thank you, Your Highness."],[6753,6865,"But none of this is my work."],[6865,7011,"It's my father's."],[7011,7199,"That's not a saddle you're working on?"],[7199,7337,"It's a saddle I'm trying to work on."],[7449,7587,"I can't produce the same quality"],[7587,7674,"as my father does."],[7716,7779,"No matter how many"],[7779,7870,"hours I spend on it."],[7991,8125,"Guess my heart just isn't in it."],[8187,8321,"What is your heart in, then?"],[8371,8559,"Everyone's heart is in something."],[8559,8684,"You're holding them."],[8826,8926,"These?"],[9009,9105,"You made these?"],[9105,9218,"I've got several now."],[9289,9376,"Boots."],[9426,9585,"A little shop, that would be enough."],[9585,9764,"You should absolutely have it."],[9764,9881,"These are amazing."],[9881,10031,"You've seen this village, right?"],[10123,10298,"My father's a saddle maker."],[10298,10431,"His before him?"],[10523,10640,"I'll be fifth generation."],[10715,10873,"Pressures of the family business."],[11007,11136,"Believe me, I get that."],[11207,11395,"Then you get that there's our dream."],[11466,11562,"Maybe one day."],[11787,12083,"And our duty."],[12805,12971,"Poor kids."],[12971,13117,"You know, I bet mum is having"],[13117,13297,"a great big laugh right now for"],[13297,13468,"sending me there."],[13530,13689,"Manipulative bitch!"],[13889,14035,"Give me your keys."],[14035,14148,"Use your own keys."],[14148,14277,"I'm a princess, Jasper."],[14277,14398,"Why would I ever need keys?"],[14398,14473,"Now give."],[14473,14606,"Your Highness, the last..."],[14606,14798,"Don't! Just save your lecture."],[14798,14927,"Okay. I'm fine. Now keys."],[15119,15236,"Was just going to remind you the last"],[15236,15370,"charity is Robert's."]],"75":[[200,287,"Damnit."],[1960,2110,"So, if writing dance troupe"],[2110,2318,"practice pieces isn't the final goal,"],[2318,2402,"then what is?"],[2402,2506,"Who says it's not?"],[2569,2631,"You know what they say"],[2631,2773,"about making assumptions."],[2802,3023,"Well, if so, then congrats. You did it."],[3111,3224,"But seriously help me out here."],[3286,3470,"When will you have arrived in your mind?"],[3586,3661,"I like that."],[3745,3962,"When will you have arrived?"],[4141,4225,"I don't know."],[4287,4504,"Come on. It's easy. For me,"],[4504,4704,"It's when I dance a solo"],[4704,4813,"at the Joyce in New York."],[4896,5080,"Now, first thing that comes to mind. Go."],[5263,5430,"Packed tents at Glastonbury."],[5501,5718,"My music moving all of them."],[5751,5876,"Like M83."],[5980,6218,"The guy writes and performs most of"],[6218,6389,"the instruments himself and,"],[6464,6535,"and he keeps"],[6535,6710,"working until it's perfect."],[6752,6860,"Nerve just popped!"],[7065,7136,"Let's go."],[7136,7265,"Come on. It'll sell out in five minutes."],[7265,7336,"We got to move."],[7336,7369,"What?"],[7369,7528,"What's going on? I'm so confused."],[7574,7653,"You'll love it."],[7690,7807,"Just trust me, okay?"],[7878,7953,"Okay."],[8425,8616,"As my faithful subject,"],[8616,8746,"by simply switching"],[8746,8887,"the old labeling process"],[8887,9071,"used by your father and grandfather,"],[9092,9296,"I'll make your whiskey the official"],[9296,9409,"royal liquor at the next"],[9409,9513,"three palace events."],[9542,9659,"Good for the town."],[9659,9838,"Good for you. Win, win."],[9968,10268,"Or here's my counter offer."],[10297,10522,"You take this, turnaround."],[10589,10727,"Leave my distillery."],[10781,10898,"Leave this village."],[10935,11102,"Get on your posh private plane and"],[11102,11282,"ride comfortably back to the palace"],[11336,11565,"while you sip a long dram of fine whiskey."],[11607,11728,"from the guy who was bold enough"],[11728,11895,"to finally talk to Her Majesty"],[11895,12099,"like the spoiled brat she is."],[12174,12349,"You see, I can no longer"],[12349,12474,"afford the old process"],[12499,12587,"because I have to pay"],[12587,12796,"so damn much in taxes in order"],[12796,12958,"that the pretty queen can buy"],[12958,13213,"all her fancy undergarments."],[13267,13463,"So no, I don't believe"],[13463,13588,"I'll be taking any orders"],[13588,13805,"from some vapid, archaic"],[13805,14089,"figurehead with no real power."]],"76":[[442,613,"I seriously have no idea what's going"],[613,709,"on right now."],[709,851,"I'm so confused."],[1873,1998,"It's Nerve."],[1998,2248,"A pop up silent dance party."],[2374,2545,"Shall we?"],[3808,3925,"You can look inside yourself"],[3925,3984,"and you can think,"],[3984,4150,"okay, I've had those problems,"],[4150,4284,"but who actually am I?"],[4313,4551,"You know, I can overcome this."],[4684,4839,"Okay, everyone, time to pair off"],[4839,5139,"into dyads for 1 to 1 discussions."],[5335,5498,"I'll take the princess."],[5518,5656,"No, Imogen, the princess"],[5656,5731,"isn't here for that."],[5731,5873,"She's just observing."],[5923,6119,"No, no. No."],[6119,6257,"It's fine."],[6257,6415,"I'd be happy to."],[7203,7362,"Appreciate what you said in the pub."],[7479,7633,"What if I change one person's life?"],[7716,7829,"It’d be a start."],[8200,8334,"Marcus, will give me a hand?"],[8384,8501,"Thank you very much."],[8784,8897,"A beautiful pair of"],[8897,9076,"handmade boots from Hale!"],[11207,11349,"Nick, this has been amazing"],[11349,11420,"really. But..."],[11420,11624,"My world wasn't enough."],[11624,11833,"No, it's not that I."],[11833,11954,"I don't know, I don't want to take"],[11954,12050,"things too fast."],[12092,12254,"No explanation necessary, Phe."],[12300,12454,"You're clearly still into him."],[12454,12692,"So deal's a deal."],[12771,12909,"This is where I back away"],[12909,13072,"until you tell me you're ready."]],"77":[[937,1045,"Well."],[1112,1220,"You sure up a whole new"],[1220,1337,"spin on Your Highness."],[1383,1479,"You holding?"],[1479,1612,"Go on. Share the wealth."],[1612,1796,"Don't my taxes pay for it?"],[1796,2071,"Taxes from, from what job?"],[2071,2171,"Sorry."],[2171,2263,"Ouch."],[2338,2522,"Fiesty Princess."],[2522,2659,"Come on."],[2659,2743,"Hook a girl up."],[2743,2980,"I can't help you, okay?"],[3039,3181,"It's probably best."],[3181,3310,"It's the third time the government"],[3310,3398,"put me in here."],[3398,3523,"Think I might try the program"],[3523,3660,"this time out of boredom?"],[3698,3823,"Just for something different."],[3923,4048,"How'd you end up here?"],[4048,4194,"My story is the same as most"],[4194,4311,"bitches in here."],[4311,4503,"Relationships with blokes just bad"],[4503,4632,"enough to keep coming back."],[4691,4895,"Too many brushes with the police while"],[4895,5045,"doing anything to keep the buzz"],[5045,5158,"going. And so on."],[5208,5375,"I'm tired of hearing it."],[5383,5579,"I'm really tired of telling it."],[5654,5729,"Oh, well you don't."],[5729,5846,"You don't have to then."],[5846,5938,"No. Hey."],[5996,6146,"It's for a Princess this time."],[6234,6430,"How often can you say that?"],[6526,6772,"It's just they have you tell the same"],[6772,6951,"bloody story every day,"],[6951,7135,"thinking it will jar something loose."],[7251,7339,"That will suddenly make you"],[7339,7510,"stop craving what you crave."],[7627,7890,"But I guess when you leave your kid"],[7890,8065,"outside in the car on a freezing"],[8065,8207,"cold night because you're inside"],[8207,8353,"getting high off your ass,"],[8386,8590,"maybe you actually do need some help."],[8732,8882,"You left your kid in the car."],[9045,9112,"No."],[9349,9445,"I was the kid."],[9733,9958,"So a shitty mum is my excuse."],[10129,10288,"What's yours?"],[10697,10930,"I just like getting high."],[11251,11368,"Yeah, I get that too."],[12419,12565,"How your mother treated you,"],[12673,12824,"it's not your fault."],[13015,13170,"Maybe once you make the choice"],[13170,13316,"to let that go"],[13403,13649,"it will get easier."],[13649,13758,"Yeah."],[14004,14121,"You too."]],"78":[[1464,1564,"Jasper,"],[1739,1843,"come in here and"],[1843,1952,"take advantage of me."],[4296,4412,"Is this what you want?"],[4942,5092,"Stand up."],[6323,6444,"Take off your dress."],[6969,7061,"Slower."],[7607,7724,"What changed your mind?"],[7912,8104,"We all have choices to make."]],"79":[[80,285,"She has a cute boyfriend."],[631,743,"I follow her too."],[810,902,"Keep your enemies close"],[902,985,"and all that."],[1231,1344,"It's fine, by the way."],[1344,1540,"I can be less concerned."],[1653,1778,"You'll go off."],[1865,2011,"You'll do what you need to,"],[2011,2145,"and then you'll come back to me."],[2270,2399,"It's what we do."],[2491,2654,"But it's always going to be you"],[2654,2804,"and me, Liam."],[3071,3179,"We're bigger than breakups,"],[3179,3262,"you and I."],[3379,3538,"Bigger than flings."],[3642,3755,"Bigger than love."],[4076,4272,"So you go ahead."],[4272,4401,"Go sort out whatever's in"],[4401,4547,"that mind of yours right now."],[4797,4927,"Better come back with your head on"],[4927,5123,"straight, because before too long,"],[5202,5340,"there'll be a crown on it."],[5732,5898,"And I'll be right beside you."],[6937,7004,"It took"],[7004,7266,"only 19 minutes for the whole distillery"],[7266,7396,"to burn to the ground."],[7433,7554,"They're saying the cause has been"],[7554,7754,"ruled an electrical fire from the"],[7754,7900,"recently installed label"],[7900,8001,"processing equipment."],[8001,8259,"Seem interested or be interested?"],[8259,8418,"You helped those people."],[8451,8622,"I helped the cows."],[8668,8789,"My father had cows."],[8868,9143,"Whiskey. Suddenly seems quite rare."],[9143,9298,"Well, switching gears to a bit of"],[9298,9465,"good news from Hale village"],[9465,9656,"as Prince Liam managed a warm"],[9656,9765,"reception there."],[9781,9948,"Several villagers say the prince could"],[9948,10073,"not have been more impressive"],[10073,10161,"in his first..."],[10186,10278,"He pulled a rabbit"],[10278,10415,"out of a hat on this one."],[10541,10674,"After yesterday, I'd have"],[10674,10795,"guessed we'd all be up in"],[10795,10933,"flames on this trip."],[11083,11237,"We need any warmth towards"],[11237,11383,"monarchy we can get."],[11391,11567,"Just received numbers from"],[11567,11692,"secret poll we asked for."],[11750,12055,"If given the vote, 45% of the people"],[12055,12121,"would vote to"],[12121,12230,"abolish the monarchy."],[12284,12555,"But that jumps another ten points"],[12555,12755,"if they were to learn that Simon himself"],[12755,12868,"suggested the referendum"],[12868,12947,"to abolish."],[13014,13193,"And if Liam was on the throne?"],[13193,13314,"The people on the fence."],[13314,13494,"They still don't know what to expect."],[13531,13777,"That's why we can't put all our eggs in"],[13777,13869,"Liam's basket."],[13906,14082,"He's too much of a wildcard."],[14082,14223,"We need to explore every"],[14223,14361,"possible option."],[14361,14553,"I could not agree more."]],"80":[[2016,2112,"Hi."],[2145,2224,"Hey."],[2279,2412,"I just got back, and I"],[2412,2512,"really wanted to see you."],[2591,2741,"So the big"],[2741,2875,"annual charity masquerade"],[2875,3042,"ball is coming up in a few days."],[3042,3184,"I very much want you to be there."],[3330,3417,"If you want to come."],[3417,3509,"Yeah."],[3509,3588,"Absolutely."],[3588,3676,"Great."],[3805,3884,"Two tickets."],[3930,3984,"Two?"],[4018,4080,"Yeah."],[4080,4185,"One for you."],[4251,4381,"And one for your boyfriend."],[4635,4735,"I'll see you there."],[5236,5369,"Liam."],[5649,5824,"Thanks."],[5824,6011,"Can't wait."]],"81":[[1526,1739,"These are nice."],[1739,1893,"You're so cute."],[1893,2043,"That's not my closet."],[2135,2427,"This is my closet."],[2844,2998,"Okay, your closet is almost"],[2998,3132,"bigger than my bedroom."],[3228,3282,"I don't even know where"],[3282,3403,"to begin to choose a dress."],[3495,3762,"Oh... actually, these aren't the dresses."],[3945,4158,"These are the dresses."],[4491,4654,"The perks of being a princess."],[4654,4771,"This is why people hate you."],[4771,4829,"Oh, I know."],[4829,5080,"Now help me pick out the best one."],[5288,5392,"I was pleased to hear Liam"],[5392,5530,"invited you to the ball."],[5593,5718,"I was less pleased to hear he"],[5718,5860,"invited your new boyfriend."],[5860,5947,"What's his name again?"],[6006,6068,"Nick."],[6068,6181,"And he's not my boyfriend."],[6181,6314,"Of course he's not your boyfriend."],[6352,6456,"\"And why?\" you ask."],[6573,6690,"It's because you're into Liam"],[6748,6948,"and he's into you but you got jealous"],[6948,7115,"and lashed out on Instagram"],[7115,7273,"and he called you on your bluff."],[7273,7424,"And so now you're bringing the boy"],[7424,7653,"not because you like said boy,"],[7728,7891,"but because you're stubborn"],[7953,8099,"and you're probably hoping"],[8099,8241,"you'll make Liam jealous."],[8291,8395,"That's not what I'm doing."],[8395,8470,"Ah-ti-ta-hat."],[8546,8733,"The bitch doth protest."],[10135,10335,"No worries. I'm good."],[10335,10543,"Oh, we all know you prefer coffee."],[10618,10706,"I thought you wanted to"],[10706,10781,"vanquish him."],[10844,11048,"Oh, I vanquished him..."],[11069,11190,"several times last night."],[11419,11524,"This one."],[11594,11724,"You have to wear this one."],[11811,11903,"It's the most beautiful"],[11903,12012,"dress I've ever seen."],[12012,12220,"Great. That one's yours."],[12220,12437,"Now help me find one."]],"82":[[159,417,"Shok, careful with that thing."],[509,642,"It's all fun and games until"],[642,730,"someone gets shot"],[730,926,"with a Maruvian arrow."],[926,1097,"Dude, relax. No-one's"],[1097,1226,"getting shot with any arrow."],[1602,1902,"Look, I get it. You're... stressed."],[1902,2023,"But, are you at least"],[2023,2144,"excited about the ball?"],[2273,2369,"Well, you know what you"],[2369,2469,"should be excited about?"],[2573,2724,"Monaco."],[2724,2890,"Thanks to yours truly, we"],[2890,2991,"are spending the weekend"],[2991,3220,"at the sickest nine-bedroom"],[3220,3349,"villa on the Cote d'Azur."],[3408,3533,"Everyone is going to be there."],[3554,3750,"The guys, the girls. I mean..."],[3750,3846,"You have to come."],[3871,3950,"We'll see."],[4017,4309,"Just say yes. Just three little letters."],[4309,4425,"Y-E-S."],[4505,4584,"Fine."],[4621,4709,"Sweet."],[4901,4968,"Low ten?"],[5038,5134,"Low ten."],[5234,5351,"What is this, 1974?"],[5376,5556,"You watch. I'm bringing it back."],[6244,6415,"Just needed a day at the spa,"],[6415,6515,"Your Majesty?"],[6523,6640,"Sometimes a girl just needs"],[6640,6761,"to be pampered, Lucius."],[7499,7658,"You two. Heel."],[7691,7916,"This is a spa, not a minefield."],[7916,8012,"Lucius will be beside me the"],[8012,8058,"whole time."],[8108,8192,"Walk away."],[8646,8763,"Treat yourself to something"],[8763,8922,"extra-special today, Lucius."],[8955,9022,"You deserve it."],[9080,9234,"I do so enjoy our little"],[9234,9430,"trips to the spa, Your Majesty."],[10607,10757,"I hope I didn't keep you waiting."],[10974,11136,"I think you know, Helly..."],[11357,11512,"I'd wait a lifetime for you."]],"83":[[543,755,"Oh, hey. You're becoming"],[755,922,"quite the little king."],[1051,1185,"Here. You probably need"],[1185,1322,"this more than I do."],[1398,1548,"And who knew the Princess had such"],[1548,1723,"a loving touch with the elderly?"],[1748,1977,"Uh, okay, I was high off my ass."],[1977,2069,"Those photos were taken"],[2069,2223,"out of context."],[2315,2595,"Well, they weren't the only ones."],[2845,3091,"I saw the photo of you and Gemma."],[3103,3220,"The Queen seems intent on"],[3220,3312,"meddling in my love life."],[3362,3504,"That's why I don't have one."],[3571,3700,"She's been completely"],[3700,3850,"out of control ever since Dad"],[3850,4013,"threatened to abolish us."],[4338,4542,"Trust me, we need this in"],[4542,4705,"order to survive Mother tonight."],[4705,4872,"Especially with Dad away."],[4889,4955,"I wonder what she'll do to"],[4955,5093,"last year's grand entrance..."],[5126,5347,"when she rode in on a unicorn."],[5539,5798,"That poor bloody horse."],[5977,6131,"Tonight shouldn't be all bad."],[6227,6311,"If memory serves,"],[6311,6373,"you've always enjoyed"],[6373,6482,"ruining a few relationships and"],[6482,6640,"breaking a few hearts."],[6732,6936,"Uh, which reminds me,"],[6936,7074,"why did you tell Ophelia"],[7074,7166,"to bring a date?"],[7178,7312,"What is wrong with you?"],[7312,7420,"Well, she’s the one who rejected me."],[7491,7650,"I was just trying to be nice."],[7650,7825,"Okay, if that's your story."],[8138,8267,"I've got to meet Ashok."],[8267,8355,"I'll see you there."],[8367,8500,"See you there."],[9464,9743,"So... it occurs to me"],[9743,9906,"that seeing as the Princess isn't"],[9906,10035,"leaving the palace this evening,"],[10035,10202,"there's no need for me to be on duty."],[10261,10394,"You're my bodyguard."],[10407,10561,"You need to be where I say"],[10561,10673,"you need to be."],[10790,11041,"And, besides, I wanted"],[11041,11212,"to see you in a tuxedo."],[11879,12071,"Really working the \"Jasper"],[12071,12254,"from Vegas\" story, aren't we?"],[12354,12463,"Still not buying it."],[12534,12625,"Hadn't we better get going,"],[12625,12759,"Your Highness?"],[12872,12972,"Oh, yes."],[13005,13097,"We wouldn't want to miss"],[13097,13264,"Mother's grand entrance."]],"84":[[1529,1709,"Ophelia looks hot."],[1825,1930,"Who's that guy?"],[2080,2197,"That's her date."],[2334,2484,"Are we okay with that?"],[2547,2797,"We are so okay with that."],[2831,2939,"Aren't we, Darling?"],[3093,3193,"You look um..."],[3289,3469,"Yeah, the the d-d-dress is... is... is..."],[3586,3761,"No, not just the dress"],[3761,3907,"but things that..."],[3907,4136,"you and the dress are doing together."],[4478,4645,"Apparently I'm speechless."],[4770,4899,"You look beautiful."],[4974,5100,"Really beautiful."],[5200,5375,"Considering how we left things,"],[5375,5508,"I feel like I should probably"],[5508,5596,"explain myself."],[5596,5775,"No need. Maybe you're"],[5775,5913,"using me, maybe you're not."],[6076,6330,"But either way I get tonight with you."],[6330,6518,"And eventually I'll wear you down."],[6605,6726,"It's a long con."],[10013,10138,"Is that a bandana you're wearing?"],[10230,10459,"Ashok, really, you are so lazy."],[10459,10751,"It's a foulard, not a bandana."],[10751,10976,"And also... my eyes are my best feature."],[13066,13312,"The Queen who would be King."],[13316,13433,"Subtle."],[13458,13554,"Well, at least she didn't glue"],[13554,13817,"a horn onto a horse this year."],[13837,14063,"I need a drink. You?"],[14359,14492,"Absolutely."],[14492,14555,"Okay."]],"85":[[1019,1115,"Are we all set for tonight?"],[1115,1232,"The Hereditary Peers"],[1232,1407,"are arriving as we speak."],[1407,1536,"While we can hope for the best,"],[1536,1687,"we must prepare for the worst."],[1687,1845,"Indeed. Just because Liam"],[1845,1966,"hasn't stepped in it already, doesn't"],[1966,2054,"mean he won't."],[2066,2162,"And the King may have backed"],[2162,2287,"off with his threat for now."],[2308,2496,"If the worst is to pass,"],[2533,2654,"we'll need the House of Lords"],[2654,2734,"on our side."],[2767,2859,"Then you'd better remind"],[2859,3017,"them what they stand to lose."],[3017,3146,"Not to worry."],[3184,3463,"Our influence will be duly felt."],[4335,4469,"The Queen will be indisposed"],[4469,4585,"for most of the evening."],[4619,4786,"Understood, Your Majesty."],[4994,5098,"Mr. Holloway."],[5123,5211,"Your Highness."],[5553,5737,"I know how you love a good ball."],[6258,6383,"You look stunning."],[6546,6713,"Won't the people miss their Queen?"],[6746,6900,"A grand entrance to kick things off,"],[6900,7046,"then a big finish at the end."],[7046,7134,"That's all they care about."],[7134,7230,"Tops and tails."],[7405,7576,"Besides, I don't want to"],[7576,7714,"be their Queen tonight."],[7789,7910,"I just want to be yours."],[8206,8297,"Come."]],"86":[[62762,62992,"I forget how beautiful it is."],[63075,63204,"Between the tours and events,"],[63204,63375,"we never really get a chance to enjoy it."],[63467,63525,"Hm."],[63621,63759,"Robert always loved it here."],[63984,64093,"How are you, my love?"],[64201,64289,"I've been worried."],[64447,64535,"I'm fine."],[64610,64710,"I have to be."],[64777,64935,"And how about Simon's threat?"],[65014,65152,"When we spoke after the funeral,"],[65152,65252,"you said he was considering"],[65252,65386,"abolishing the Monarchy."],[65461,65632,"You know the rules. We don't"],[65632,65749,"talk about those things."],[65911,66011,"Well, in that case, what is"],[66011,66203,"it the Queen would like to do?"],[66203,66374,"Well, I can't speak for the Queen."],[66449,66549,"But as for me..."],[66704,66837,"Can we just walk for a while?"],[66966,67112,"Whatever my girl wants."],[67300,67392,"Don't look now, but David"],[67392,67534,"Beckham just smiled at you."],[67575,67663,"Seriously?"],[67684,67842,"Total David Beckham smile."],[67884,67959,"Madness."],[68080,68197,"Yeah, it really is."],[68247,68380,"Luckily for you,"],[68380,68530,"I'm an expert wallflower."],[68606,68718,"First few dances I went to,"],[68718,68818,"I was absolutely terrified"],[68818,68939,"of embarrassing myself."],[68960,69073,"Believe me, I can relate."],[69144,69214,"What changed?"],[69214,69290,"The right song came on"],[69290,69515,"and I just... had to dance to it."],[69602,69736,"Made me realize two things."],[69773,70003,"One, the power of a good song."],[70032,70140,"And, two..."],[70261,70395,"sometimes you've just gotta jump in."],[70507,70578,"Even when your head is"],[70578,70670,"telling you otherwise."],[70874,71029,"Okay, there's no way you can be"],[71029,71283,"this stable, self-aware, nice."],[71342,71458,"You forgot to mention handsome."],[71575,71688,"And an excellent dancer."],[71755,71959,"Come on. Let's go."],[72885,73022,"Looks like they're having fun."],[73102,73260,"Yeah. I guess."],[73415,73519,"Let's have another drink."],[73577,73698,"Shok, what's that shot"],[73698,73790,"you were telling us about?"],[73807,73965,"The Flaming Lamborghini."],[73965,74082,"What in God's dear name"],[74082,74249,"is the Flaming Lamborghini?"],[74307,74457,"I thought you'd never ask."],[75229,75316,"Dance with me."],[75429,75479,"I thought I was"],[75479,75583,"supposed to be working."],[75650,75825,"You are. And right now I need"],[75825,76000,"you to work on protecting me"],[76000,76159,"from the Grand Duke of Norway’s"],[76159,76297,"wandering hands."],[76392,76530,"I really do worry about your"],[76530,76785,"ability to protect my body, Jasper."],[77214,77439,"Awkward transition into a slow jam."],[77602,77723,"I say we roll with it."]],"87":[[2014,2155,"I thought a picnic was in order."],[2193,2376,"Like our first date in the hayloft."],[2518,2635,"Well, we couldn't have very well"],[2635,2752,"let my father catch us."],[2814,2944,"God forbid he'd find out his"],[2944,3081,"daughter was dating the help."],[3094,3131,"Ha."],[3265,3390,"Oh, daisies."],[3707,3786,"I always think of you"],[3786,3845,"when I see them."],[3945,4107,"I couldn't afford a proper bouquet."],[4149,4199,"No."],[4262,4366,"But then you'd braid them into"],[4366,4554,"such lovely little crowns for me."],[4700,4812,"You were my Queen long"],[4812,4946,"before you were theirs."],[10722,10947,"Come with me, bodyguard."],[11323,11406,"Ophelia."],[11798,11936,"Roll with it?"],[11978,12132,"Can't argue with that."]],"88":[[136,336,"You must be Nick. Good to meet you."],[357,441,"Yeah, you too."],[520,707,"Uh... Your Royal Highness."],[707,774,"Just..."],[799,916,"call me Liam."],[916,1033,"Come on, let's get you a drink."],[1458,1679,"The new boyfriend is hot."],[1763,1871,"What's his story?"],[1925,2105,"Nick? He's a musician."],[2167,2351,"Rock stars are amazing in bed."],[2397,2555,"Good for you."],[2693,2868,"We drink the good stuff in here."],[3018,3106,"You're welcome."],[3398,3477,"Shots or beer?"],[3560,3623,"Both?"],[3623,3669,"Cheers."],[3840,3911,"Cool."],[4023,4111,"I'm thinking maybe no"],[4111,4219,"shots for you, mayonnaise."],[4386,4445,"I think Gemma"],[4445,4536,"drugged my champagne."],[4570,4641,"I'll be back."],[4753,4853,"Sounds like she got in a little"],[4853,5024,"over her head at the Garden Party."],[5104,5245,"Said you took good care of her."],[5400,5587,"Just being a good friend. Cheers."],[7247,7347,"Pull my hair. Come on,"],[7347,7439,"you know how I like it."],[8273,8390,"I want you inside me."],[8457,8574,"Right here, right now."],[9045,9178,"That's not what this is."],[9266,9374,"What?"],[9391,9621,"You don't control this. I do."],[10868,11009,"What the hell was that?"],[11180,11331,"The tunnel and the tuxedo and the"],[11331,11489,"dancing. That's not what this is."],[11623,11710,"You wanted me to"],[11710,11877,"be your little sex slave."],[11877,11998,"You're blackmailing me."],[11998,12115,"That is what this is."],[12115,12152,"Is it?"],[12240,12315,"Of course it is."],[12465,12569,"Well, if that's what this is,"],[12569,12682,"then go ahead and end it."],[12932,13157,"Go into that room and tell everybody"],[13157,13283,"how I'm blackmailing you."]],"89":[[551,597,"If that's what this"],[597,701,"really is, then end it."],[776,868,"Tell them all."],[1035,1139,"Go on. Do it."],[1247,1343,"Fine."],[1389,1460,"I will."],[1890,2198,"I have something important to say."],[2277,2565,"Something that will change everything."],[3233,3500,"Those shoes with that dress?"],[3500,3775,"Really, bitch?"],[4463,4659,"Gentlemen, for years the"],[4659,4855,"aristocracy ran this country."],[4876,5180,"And, if I may be so bold, for the better."],[5180,5339,"Hear, hear."],[5339,5597,"But there are rumors of a"],[5597,5698,"referendum to"],[5698,5864,"abolish the Monarchy."],[6027,6332,"If and when such a bill is passed,"],[6332,6490,"we must band together to"],[6490,6732,"save this country from itself."],[6732,6915,"I'm relying on the House of Lords"],[6915,7061,"to delay a referendum"],[7061,7249,"at all costs."],[7320,7583,"I'm sure I don't need to remind you"],[7583,7846,"that our lifestyle is a"],[7846,8054,"lifestyle worth preserving."],[8676,8801,"Because if the Monarchy"],[8801,8917,"goes down,"],[8917,9147,"we all go down with it."],[9201,9426,"Luckily for you, tonight the only"],[9426,9689,"thing going down are your servers."],[9810,9935,"After four hours,"],[9935,10089,"seek medical attention."],[11299,11495,"Most of these men are happy enough"],[11495,11637,"with a common whore, but"],[11637,11920,"as for me, I prefer my whores to be..."],[12071,12192,"uncommon."],[12279,12438,"Go to my room and wait for me."],[12500,12755,"And, remember, enthusiasm counts."]],"90":[[28,257,"Phantogram's new album is awesome."],[257,324,"If you like that, you should"],[324,474,"go back and listen to their EP."],[511,637,"It's way underrated."],[674,841,"I do hate to interrupt,"],[841,991,"but I love this song and"],[991,1137,"I could really use a warm body."],[1304,1442,"Nick, would you mind terribly?"],[1663,1779,"Is this where you ask me to dance"],[1779,1850,"and then the jocks lock me"],[1850,1950,"in the trunk of a car?"],[2013,2238,"Dance floor, McFly. Now."],[2922,2993,"Gemma."],[3135,3247,"You're up to something."],[3348,3418,"What?"],[3485,3644,"I'm just doing you a favor."],[3681,3831,"You obviously want to dance with"],[3831,3927,"Ophelia. I'm merely"],[3927,4040,"giving you the chance."],[4077,4203,"The sooner you realize that"],[4203,4399,"she's really nothing special,"],[4415,4628,"the sooner you come back to me."],[5416,5525,"Where's Nick?"],[5700,5846,"He's dancing with Gemma."],[6184,6292,"Dance with me?"],[8574,8736,"Nick seems like a nice guy."],[8778,8957,"Yeah, he really is."],[9253,9395,"Kid knows his music."],[9420,9487,"We actually like"],[9487,9612,"a lot of the same bands."],[9662,9825,"That's... great."],[10217,10380,"And he's funny, too. I can see why..."],[10380,10580,"The least you could do is not like him."],[10638,10793,"Ophelia, he's your boyfriend."],[10793,10880,"I'm trying to be nice."],[10901,11084,"Well, I wish you'd stop being so nice."],[11084,11281,"For the record, he's not my boyfriend."],[11372,11522,"Oh, my bad."],[11556,11593,"I meant that guy"],[11593,11706,"you made out with on Instagram."],[11760,11860,"Well considering that photo of"],[11860,11965,"you and Gemma grinding"],[11965,12044,"on the plane tour..."],[12044,12131,"It wasn't like that."],[12131,12248,"Well, I never made out with Nick."],[12248,12352,"I didn't even kiss him."],[12352,12411,"Okay, fine."],[12453,12498,"Fine."],[12498,12569,"Good."],[12569,12661,"Great."],[12757,12865,"Thanks for the dance."],[12865,12941,"Sure."],[13170,13266,"Ophelia, your earrings"],[13266,13341,"are amazing."],[13341,13449,"Thank you."],[13712,13967,"You two are so good together."]],"91":[[86,261,"The perfect storm."],[511,619,"The day my father came back"],[619,711,"from the bank."],[770,882,"The day he realized we were"],[882,1078,"we were going to lose everything."],[1195,1308,"First Black Monday,"],[1324,1466,"then the BSE crisis,"],[1512,1616,"then the interest rates."],[1721,1854,"That's what he called it."],[1962,2171,"The perfect storm."],[2563,2621,"I was just wondering"],[2621,2671,"what my life"],[2671,2742,"would have been like if"],[2742,2888,"not for those three words."],[3055,3205,"What our life might have been like..."],[3310,3443,"had my mother not pushed"],[3443,3581,"me into marrying Simon."],[3793,3902,"\"What if?\" has a way of"],[3902,4019,"finding us, doesn't it?"],[4269,4465,"I had a dream about Henry last night."],[4465,4757,"He visited me like a tragic ghost."],[4970,5099,"You were in a war."],[5145,5316,"You saved countless lives."],[5353,5512,"Henry's death wasn't your fault."],[5574,5670,"He had no family and"],[5670,5800,"no-one else but me."],[5958,6142,"I couldn't save him."],[6375,6488,"Sometimes I look at the medals"],[6488,6555,"and commendations"],[6555,6721,"and I wish that I could"],[6721,6871,"go back for one day..."],[6997,7155,"do everything differently."],[7193,7318,"They gave you those medals"],[7318,7564,"because you were a hero."],[7685,7868,"Not to him I wasn't. Not that day."],[8135,8269,"Anyway, the point is,"],[8269,8461,"the past is the past."],[8561,8723,"We don't get to go back."],[8869,9061,"All we have left is today."],[9366,9524,"I know you don't want to discuss it,"],[9524,9616,"but you should know"],[9616,9774,"if there is a referendum"],[9774,9916,"to abolish the Monarchy..."],[10100,10258,"I know which way I'll vote."],[10413,10596,"Tonight could be every night."]],"92":[[455,563,"What's wrong with you?"],[646,730,"The Sultan of Bhondai"],[730,851,"just cock-blocked us."],[851,922,"What?"],[1009,1168,"The villa in Monaco is out."],[1193,1351,"We got bumped."],[1351,1501,"Are we okay with that?"],[1581,1706,"We don't have a choice."],[1706,1852,"Of course we do."],[1852,1927,"You know what trumps"],[1927,2056,"the Sultan of Bhondai?"],[2131,2302,"The future King of England."],[3141,3220,"Your Highness."],[3220,3299,"My Lord, I take it"],[3299,3433,"you're enjoying yourself?"],[3433,3579,"Indeed, Your Highness. And"],[3579,3812,"while tonight has been..."],[3816,3925,"lovely..."],[3983,4087,"I do so hate looking a"],[4087,4196,"gift horse in the mouth."],[4196,4317,"Oh, stop being so bloody"],[4317,4475,"English and spit it out."],[4475,4559,"Very well, sir."],[4588,4726,"Public sentiment towards the"],[4726,4992,"Monarchy is at an all-time low."],[5055,5230,"If a vote on a referendum is"],[5230,5464,"brought to the floor, it will not only pass,"],[5464,5610,"I believe it will do so"],[5610,5752,"with a huge majority."],[5752,5902,"And if the House of Lords"],[5902,6106,"does try to delay such a bill,"],[6106,6260,"there will be rioting in the streets."],[6260,6423,"They will have our heads."],[6423,6548,"Which is why I've taken steps to"],[6548,6736,"ensure that if such a bill passes,"],[6736,6949,"it won't be with a sweeping majority."],[6969,7095,"Forgive me, Your Highness, but"],[7095,7278,"how on earth can you ensure that?"],[7303,7583,"I believe you know James Holloway."],[7704,7816,"I do indeed."],[7816,8029,"Well, rest assured, Mr. Holloway"],[8029,8279,"is very much in bed with us."],[8321,8450,"The Duke of York"],[8450,8604,"and James Holloway?"],[8688,8838,"Strange bedfellows."],[8842,8984,"Needless to say, you do"],[8984,9172,"your duty, we'll do ours."],[9209,9397,"You can count on us, Your Highness."],[9426,9501,"I knew you'd come to"],[9501,9605,"see things my way."],[9877,10010,"People always do."]],"93":[[3